《{{tsl|en|Metroid Prime 3: Corruption|银河战士Prime 3：堕落}}》在北美被宣传为首发的游戏，但它的发行最终被推迟到了2007年8月27日。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/790/790231p1.html |title=Nintendo's America Summer Line-up |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date= |accessdate=2007-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070611152942/http://wii.ign.com/articles/790/790231p1.html |archive-date=2007-06-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[岩田聰|岩田聰]]最初也希望《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥X|任天堂明星大亂鬥X]]》也能成为首发游戏。

{{reflist|group=Note}}

==硬件==
[[File:NintendoStack.jpg|thumb]]、[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]、北美版[[超級任天堂|SNES]]和歐美版[[红白机|NES]]的尺寸比较|alt=一叠电子游戏机，其中任天堂Wii是尺寸最小的]]

Wii是任天堂当时最小的家用电子游戏机，当垂直放置时，Wii宽44[[毫米|毫米]]、高157毫米、长215.4毫米，稍微大于三个{{tsl|en|keep case||DVD光盘盒}}叠在一起。附赠的底座宽55.4毫米、高44毫米、长225.6毫米。主机重为1.2[[千克|千克]]，<ref name="WiiWeight">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/127859/a_closer_look_at_the_nintendo_wii.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080205074335/http://www.pcworld.com/article/id%2C127859-page%2C1/article.html |archivedate=2008-02-05 |title=A Closer Look at the Nintendo Wii |first=Danny |last=Allen |magazine=PC World |date=2006-11-17 |accessdate=2007-03-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>使它成为了在三个主要[[第七世代遊戲機|第七世代遊戲機]]中最轻便的一个。Wii可以以垂直或水平方式摆放。Wii和其附件的所有型号编码均以“RVL-”开头，代表着主机的[[代号|代号]]：“Revolution”。<ref>{{cite news|title=Wii controller world tour|page=8|publisher={{tsl|en|Nintendo Gamer||NGamer}}|date=2007-07-13}}</ref>

主机正面拥有一个吸入式光驱，光驱被透明塑料环绕并可以发光，光驱支持12厘米[[任天堂光盘#Wii光碟|Wii光盘]]和8厘米[[任天堂光盘#任天堂GameCube遊戲光碟|任天堂GameCube游戏光碟]]。<ref name=Salon>{{cite web|title=Compatibility of the Nintendo Wii|url=http://techtips.salon.com/compatibility-nintendo-wii-2284.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110526042233/http://techtips.salon.com/compatibility-nintendo-wii-2284.html|archivedate=2011-05-26|first=Benny|last=Taylor|website=Salon|accessdate=2020-01-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>（在韩国销售的所有机型以及其他地区的后续机型不支持GameCube光盘。）<ref name="Wii2.0"/><ref name=GameSpotKr>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.co.kr/wii/news/0,39051458,39400693-39098642p,00.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080618070527/http://www.gamespot.co.kr/wii/news/0%2C39051458%2C39400693-39098642p%2C00.htm |archivedate=2008-06-18 |title=한국판 Wii, 타 국가게임 '사용불가' |author=김민규 기자 |website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |language=ko |date=2008-04-14 |accessdate=2008-09-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="EurogamerReview" />光驱周围的灯光在主机开启时会短暂的点亮，并会在主机通过[[WiiConnect24|WiiConnect24]]接收到数据时闪烁。<ref name=NintendoUK>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Wii/Get-Connected/WiiConnect24/WiiConnect24-Wii-Online-Wii-Nintendo-UK-626436.html|title=WiiConnect24|publisher=Nintendo Europe|accessdate=2020-01-20|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204230556/https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Wii/Get-Connected/WiiConnect24/WiiConnect24-Wii-Online-Wii-Nintendo-UK-626436.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在主机进行系统更新后（System Menu 3.0及以上），光驱周围的灯光也会在吸入或弹出光盘时点亮。<ref name=Update3>{{cite web|url=https://gizmodo.com/286691/wii-gets-a-firmware-update-1-feature-is-a-clock|title=Wii Gets a Firmware Update, #1 Feature is a Clock…|website=Gizmodo|access-date=2020-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007184548/https://gizmodo.com/286691/wii-gets-a-firmware-update-1-feature-is-a-clock|archive-date=2018-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>当没有任何WiiConnect24信息时，灯光会保持熄灭状态。灯光也不会在游戏运行或使用其他功能时点亮。主机背面拥有两个[[USB|USB]]接口<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.techradar.com/news/gaming/consoles/eight-things-you-didn-t-know-the-wii-could-do-270149|title=Eight things you didn't know the Wii could do|work=TechRadar|access-date=2018-10-10|language=EN-GB|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011014110/https://www.techradar.com/news/gaming/consoles/eight-things-you-didn-t-know-the-wii-could-do-270149|archive-date=2018-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>主机正面的SD卡插槽盖后方拥有一个SD卡插槽。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Support/Wii/Usage/SD-Cards/Using-an-SD-Card/Using-an-SD-Card-239906.html|title=Using an SD Card|website=Nintendo of Europe GmbH|language=en-GB|access-date=2018-10-10}}</ref>

[[Wii發售日列表|Wii首发版]]主机盒子内含Wii主机、一个能让主机垂直摆放的底座、一个可以安装在底座上的透明的类圆形圆盘，用以稳定垂直摆放的主机、一个[[Wii遥控器|Wii遥控器]]、一个[[Wii遙控器|Nunchuk]]附加控制器、一个[[Wii|红外感应条]]、一个可以安装在感应条上的支架、一个外置[[電源供應|电源适配器]]、两颗[[AA電池|AA電池]]、一个拥有[[RCA端子|RCA端子]]的[[AV端子|复合AV视频线缆]]、<ref name=launch>{{cite web|url=http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-10921_7-6637970-4.html|title=Nintendo Wii release details: Nov. 19, $250 with a game included|website=CNET|date=2006-09-14|first=David|last=Rudden|access-date=2012-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723190318/http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-10921_7-6637970-4.html|archive-date=2013-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>一个{{tsl|en|SCART||SCART}}转换器（仅在欧洲销售的主机中提供）、操作手册和游戏《[[Wii_Sports|Wii Sports]]》的副本（仅在美洲和欧洲销售的主机中提供）。复合视频以及其它种类的视频线缆另行销售。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/745/745708p1.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061115004549/http://wii.ign.com/articles/745/745708p1.html|archive-date=2006-11-15|title=IGN: Wii Sports Review|date=2006-11-15|access-date=2018-10-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

Wii的光驱无法播放[[DVD-Video|DVD视频]]、[[DVD-Audio|DVD音频]]或[[CD|CD]]光盘。2006年，任天堂宣布将会在2007年发布一款新版本的Wii，其可以播放DVD视频光盘。<ref name="DVD-Wii 2007" />但是，任天堂因需要满足对最初机型的需求而推迟了新款主机的发布。<ref name="No DVD-Wii 2007">{{cite web|url=http://www.reghardware.co.uk/2007/11/09/wii_dvd_playback_delayed/|title=Nintendo confirms Wii DVD support coming|accessdate=2007-11-28|last=Sherwood|first=James|date=2007-11-09|work=[[The_Register|The Register]] Hardware|publisher=Situation Publishing|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080731070716/http://www.reghardware.co.uk/2007/11/09/wii_dvd_playback_delayed/|archive-date=2008-07-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>任天堂声明称，播放这些光盘“需要的不仅仅是系统固件升级”才能实现，它们也无法通过任何方式来对最初版Wii进行硬件升级来实现；<ref name="DVD-Wii 2007">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/features/confirmed-nintendo-to-release-dvd-enabled-wii-in-2007/69689/?biz=1|publisher=GameDaily BIZ|title=Confirmed: Nintendo to Release DVD-Enabled Wii in 2007|first=James|last=Brightman|accessdate=2006-11-14|date=2006-11-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100901065337/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/features/confirmed-nintendo-to-release-dvd-enabled-wii-in-2007/69689/?biz=1|archivedate=2010-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>后来，随着2013年Wii的停产，这一推迟发布最终也变成了取消。尽管如此，第三方开发者后来通过开发{{tsl|en|Wii homebrew||Wii自制软件}}为Wii添加了DVD光盘播放功能，并无需任何对Wii进行任何硬件更改。<ref name=homebrewdvd>{{cite web|url=http://hackmii.com/2008/08/libdi-and-the-dvdx-installer/|title=libdi and the DVDX installer|publisher=HackMii|date=2008-08-12|accessdate=2008-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081006035415/http://hackmii.com/2008/08/libdi-and-the-dvdx-installer/|archive-date=2008-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii也可以被[[駭客文化|黑客攻击]]，使主机拥有者能让Wii以非开发商预计的方式运作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maxconsole.net/?mode=news&newsid=21266|title=The 'unhackable' Wii gets hacked, '30 wire' D2C mod on its way|publisher=MaxConsole|date=2007-09-28|accessdate=2007-11-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071027032050/http://www.maxconsole.net/?mode=news&newsid=21266|archivedate=2007-10-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii拥有许多品牌的[[破解芯片|破解芯片]]。<ref name=Mod>{{cite web|title=New Wii drives breaking modchips, hearts, legs|url=https://www.engadget.com/2008/12/10/new-wii-drives-breaking-modchips-hearts-legs/|first=Joshua|last=Topolsky|date=2008-12-10|accessdate=2012-09-13|work=Engadget|publisher=AOL Inc.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121207004709/http://www.engadget.com/2008/12/10/new-wii-drives-breaking-modchips-hearts-legs/|archive-date=2012-12-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

虽然任天堂在发布前展示了白色、黑色、银色、灰绿色和红色的游戏机和Wii遥控器，<ref name="Rev colors console">{{cite web|url=http://www.kotaku.com.au/2012/10/wheres-my-lime-green-wii-nintendo/|publisher=Gawker Media|work=Kotaku Australia|title=NINTENDO Where’s My Lime Green Wii, Nintendo?|date=2012-10-06|accessdate=2012-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007084422/http://www.kotaku.com.au/2012/10/wheres-my-lime-green-wii-nintendo/|archive-date=2012-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>它在最初两年半的销售中只有白色的版本。2009年8月，黑色版本Wii在日本上市，<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo Selling Black Wii in Japan This Summer|url=http://kotaku.com/5278279/nintendo-selling-black-wii-in-japan-this-summer|publisher=Kotaku|date=2009-06-04|accessdate=2009-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090607070623/http://kotaku.com/5278279/nintendo-selling-black-wii-in-japan-this-summer|archive-date=2009-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/wii/console/index.html|language=ja|title=Wii|publisher=Nintendo|date=2009-08-01|accessdate=2009-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090805151836/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/wii/console/index.html|archive-date=2009-08-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年11月，黑色版本Wii在欧洲上市，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/2009/limited_edition_black_wii_bundle_announced_for_europe_including_wii_sports_resort_and_wii_motionplus_14833.html|title=Limited Edition Black Wii bundle announced for Europe, including Wii Sports Resort and Wii MotionPlus|publisher=Nintendo|date=2009-10-20| accessdate=2009-10-20}}</ref>2010年5月9日，黑色版本在北美上市。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.businesswire.com/portal/site/home/permalink/?ndmViewId=news_view&newsId=20100503005799&newsLang=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100507174758/http://www.businesswire.com/portal/site/home/permalink/?ndmViewId=news_view&newsId=20100503005799&newsLang=en|archive-date=2010-05-07|title=ADDING MULTIMEDIA Nintendo to Include Wii Sports Resort, Wii MotionPlus with All New Wii Systems|publisher=Business Wire|date=2010-05-07|access-date=2018-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年11月11日，任天堂在日本推出了一款红色的Wii的套装，以纪念《[[超级马里奥兄弟|超级马里奥兄弟]]》25周年，<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo Wii turns red with glee for Super Mario's 25th anniversarii|url=https://www.engadget.com/2010/10/07/nintendo-wii-turns-red-with-glee-for-super-marios-25th-annivers/|publisher=Engadget|date=2010-10-07|accessdate=2010-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101009111733/http://www.engadget.com/2010/10/07/nintendo-wii-turns-red-with-glee-for-super-marios-25th-annivers/|archive-date=2010-10-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年10月29日，限量版红色Wii捆绑套装在欧洲发售，主机中包含预先安装的《[[大金刚_(游戏)|大金刚]]》游戏以及《[[新超级马里奥兄弟Wii|新超级马里奥兄弟Wii]]》和《Wii Sports》游戏光盘。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://kotaku.com/5660577/europe-gets-red-wii-bundle|title=Europe Gets Red Wii Bundle|last=Plunkett|first=Luke|work=Kotaku|date=2010-10-11|access-date=2018-09-15|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180916022759/https://kotaku.com/5660577/europe-gets-red-wii-bundle|archive-date=2018-09-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/104278-Europe-Continues-to-Celebrate-Mario-With-Shiny-Red-Wii|title=Europe Continues to Celebrate Mario With Shiny Red Wii|work=The Escapist|date=2010-10-12|access-date=2018-10-10|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011053522/https://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/104278-Europe-Continues-to-Celebrate-Mario-With-Shiny-Red-Wii|archive-date=2018-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>套装中附赠了Wii遥控器Plus，其内置Wii Motion Plus技术。<ref name=":1" />2010年11月7日，红色版本Wii套装在北美发售，内含《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》、《Wii Sports》和Wii遥控器Plus。<ref>{{cite web|title=Anniversary Bundles and Wii Remote Plus Confirmed for US|url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/24335|publisher=Nintendo World Report|date=2010-10-21|access-date=2010-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714185419/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/24335|archive-date=2011-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/10/21/red-wii-and-dsi-xl-bundles-wii-remote-plus-and-flingsmash-in-n/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101024192034/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/10/21/red-wii-and-dsi-xl-bundles-wii-remote-plus-and-flingsmash-in-n/|archive-date=2010-10-24|title=Red Wii and DSi XL bundles, Wii Remote Plus, and FlingSmash in North America Nov. 7|publisher=Joystiq|date=2010-10-24|access-date=2018-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2007年7月11日，任天堂在[[E3电子娱乐展|E3 2007]]上公布了{{tsl|en|Wii Balance Board||Wii平衡板}}和《[[Wii_Fit|Wii Fit]]》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.consolewatcher.com/2007/07/stay-fit-with-nintendo-wii-balance-board/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080321044858/http://www.consolewatcher.com/2007/07/stay-fit-with-nintendo-wii-balance-board/|archivedate=2008-03-21|title=Stay fit with Wii Balance Board|date=2007-11-12|publisher=Console Watcher|accessdate=2020-01-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii平衡板为一个用于Wii的无线[[晃板|平衡板]]外设，并拥有多个压力感应器，用于感测用户的{{tsl|en|center of mass||平衡中心}}。<ref>{{cite video|people=Shigeru Miyamoto (Interviewed)|date=2007-07-12|title=E3 2007: Shigeru Miyamoto Video Interview|url=http://uk.media.wii.ign.com/articles/804/804464/vids_1.html|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2007-07-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070816211448/http://uk.media.wii.ign.com/articles/804/804464/vids_1.html|archivedate=2007-08-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[万代南梦宫娱乐|万代南梦宫娱乐]]也生产了一个类似的垫子控制器，其相较于Wii平衡板拥有更简单的构造。<ref name=NamcoMat>{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/873/873470p1.html|title=Namco Bandai Take to the Mat|website=IGN|date=2008-05-13|accessdate=2012-09-13|last=Robinson|first=Martin|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080720170656/http://wii.ign.com/articles/873/873470p1.html|archive-date=2008-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

===Wii遥控器===
[[File:Wiimote-in-Hands.jpg|thumb]]、[[Wii遥控器|Wii遥控器]]和带子|alt=两种类型的Wii遥控器，两只手每只手握一种]]
[[File:Wii-Classic-Controller-White.jpg|thumb]]
{{Main|Wii遥控器}}
Wii遥控器是主机的主要[[游戏控制器|控制器]]。当Wii遥控器对着感应条的[[发光二极管|发光二极管]]时，其能使用内置的[[加速規|加速規]]和[[红外线|红外线]]检测器来感应遥控器在[[三維空間|三維空間]]中的位置。<ref name="remote_accel">{{cite web|last=Wisniowski|first=Howard|url=http://www.analog.com/en/press-release/May_09_2006_ADI_Nintendo_Collaboration/press.html|title=Analog Devices And Nintendo Collaboration Drives Video Game Innovation With iMEMS Motion Signal Processing Technology|publisher=Analog Devices, Inc.|date=2006-05-09|accessdate=2009-01-31|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090625055416/http://www.analog.com/en/press-release/May_09_2006_ADI_Nintendo_Collaboration/press.html|archive-date=2009-06-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Nintendo and PixArt">{{cite web|url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/newsArt.cfm?artid=11557|title=Nintendo and PixArt Team Up|publisher=Nintendo World Report|last=Castaneda|first=Karl|date=2006-05-13|accessdate=2007-02-24|language=en|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65cjnnd71?url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/11557|archive-date=2012-02-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>这个设计使用户能通过手部动作和按钮来控制主机，Wii遥控器通过[[藍牙|藍牙]]连接到主机，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/systems/technical_details_1072.html|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120904122140/http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/systems/technical_details_1072.html|archive-date=2012-09-04|title=Wii: Technical Details|accessdate=2009-02-22|publisher=Nintendo of Europe|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>拥有大约{{convert|30|ft|adj=on|abbr=on}}的连接距离。<ref name="hard_inf">{{cite web|url=http://wii.nintendo.com/controller.jsp|title=Nintendo Wii – Hardware Information|publisher=Nintendo|accessdate=2006-05-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080212080618/http://wii.nintendo.com/controller.jsp|archivedate=2008-02-12|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>支持{{tsl|en|Haptic technology||振动}}功能，并内置了一个扬声器。<ref name="Ops Man 6465">{{Cite book|title=Wii Operations Manual: Channels and Settings|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/downloads/WiiOpMn_setup.pdf|format=PDF|pages=64–65|id=C/RVL-USZ-4|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]]|year=2008|language=en|access-date=2020-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023052434/https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/downloads/WiiOpMn_setup.pdf|archive-date=2019-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>任天堂设计了一个可移除的[[Wii_Remote|腕带]]外设，用以防止玩家无意摔落或甩出Wii遥控器。任天堂随后还推出了加强版的腕带和[[Wii遙控器|Wii遥控器套]]来提高抓握强度和保护。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/meGSAugqYGKxlEMVLDtePEEQweFFdtSM|title=Nintendo announces new Wii Remote Jacket accessory|date=2007-09-01|publisher=Nintendo|accessdate=2007-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071214005824/http://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/meGSAugqYGKxlEMVLDtePEEQweFFdtSM|archive-date=2007-12-14|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Wii遥控器附件可以通过一个位于遥控器底部的{{tsl|en|Proprietary hardware||专有}}接口连接到遥控器，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/nintendo-wiimote-change-before-after-puberty|title=Nintendo Wiimote change: before & after puberty|website=Destructoid|author=Niero|date=2006-06-14|accessdate=2007-03-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070204033225/http://www.destructoid.com/nintendo-wiimote-change-before-after-puberty|archivedate=2007-02-04|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>例如[[Wii遙控器|Nunchuk]]：一个内置加速规和一个[[类比摇杆|类比摇杆]]，两个扳机按键的附加控制器。<ref name="noe_launch">{{cite magazine|last=Wales|first=Matt|date=2006-05-22|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=140333&skip=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060615010501/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=140333&skip=yes|archivedate=2006-06-15|title=Reports claim Wii to slap down 16 at launch|magazine=Computer and Video Games|accessdate=2006-05-25|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>一个内置[[陀螺仪|陀螺仪]]的扩展附件{{tsl|en|Wii MotionPlus||Wii MotionPlus}}可以加强Wii遥控器的动作感应精度；MotionPlus功能最后添加进了新版本的Wii遥控器，并成为Wii遥控器Plus。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2008/jul/17/moreonwiismotionplus|title=More on Wii's MotionPlus|last=Stuart|first=Keith|date=2008-07-17|work=The Guardian|access-date=2017-09-23|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923194241/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2008/jul/17/moreonwiismotionplus|archive-date=2017-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Iwata Asks 1">{{cite web |title=The Gyro Sensor: A New Sense Of Control |url=http://us.wii.com/iwata_asks/wiimotionplus/vol1_page1.jsp |work=Iwata Asks: Wii MotionPlus |publisher=Nintendo |page=1 |accessdate=2009-06-04 |quote=No, the intention was to integrate the two from the very start. This is why when we use the term Wii MotionPlus, we are referring to the accessory with the Wii MotionPlus Jacket attached. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110217194342/http://us.wii.com/iwata_asks/wiimotionplus/vol1_page1.jsp |archivedate=2011-02-17 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2374174,00.asp|title=Nintendo Wii Remote Plus|last=|first=|date=|website=PC Magazine|language=en|access-date=2017-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923095937/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2374174,00.asp|archive-date=2017-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>在{{tsl|en|E3 2009||E3 2009}}上，任天堂还展示了一个“{{tsl|en|Heart rate monitor||活力传感器}}”外设，可以检测玩家的脉搏。在2013年的问答采访中，岩田聪透露，活力传感器已经被搁置，因为在内部测试中发现，该设备并不是所有用户都能使用，而且用途过于狭窄。<ref name="Vitalityend">{{Cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-07-05-nintendo-explains-wii-vitality-sensor-cancellation|title=Nintendo explains Wii Vitality Sensor cancellation|last=Phillips|first=Tom|date=2013-07-05|website=Eurogamer|language=en-GB|access-date=2017-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911161605/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-07-05-nintendo-explains-wii-vitality-sensor-cancellation|archive-date=2017-09-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Wii{{tsl|en|Classic Controller||经典控制器}}是一个用于Wii的控制器，其类似于普通游戏控制器，其可以用于在Wii上游玩Virtual Console游戏。

===存储器===
Wii主机内置512[[百萬位元組|MB]]不可移除[[闪存|闪存]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/1017136/wii-console-specs-unveiled|title=Wii console specs unveiled|publisher={{tsl|en|The Inquirer||The Inquirer}}|date=2006-08-01|first=Dean|last=Pullen|access-date=2018-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011133335/https://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/1017136/wii-console-specs-unveiled|archive-date=2018-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>和一个用于增加外部储存空间的SD卡插槽，SD卡可以用于上传照片、备份[[游戏存档|游戏存档]]和存放下载的[[Virtual_Console|Virtual Console]]和[[WiiWare|WiiWare]]游戏。要使用SD卡槽传输游戏存档，主机必须进行系统[[修補程式|升级]]。系统可以在Wii选项菜单通过互联网连接进行升级，或插入一张内含系统升级数据的游戏光盘。SD卡中存储的Virtual Console数据只能恢复到原备份的Wii主机中。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/wii/en_na/data.jsp|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080522080838/https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/wii/en_na/data.jsp|archive-date=2008-05-22|title={{!}} Nintendo - Customer Service {{!}} Wii - Data Management|date=2008-05-22|access-date=2018-10-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>SD卡也可以通过存储[[MP3|MP3]]文件来创建自制游戏内音乐（最初出现于游戏《{{tsl|en|Excite Truck|激情卡車}}》）<ref name="Excite Truck Custom Soundtrack Confirmed">{{cite web|date=2006-11-10|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/745/745360p1.html|title=Excite Truck Custom Soundtrack Confirmed|website=IGN|accessdate=2006-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070126085904/http://wii.ign.com/articles/745/745360p1.html|archive-date=2007-01-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和用于使用在[[Wii频道|照片频道]]中的创建幻灯片放映功能。1.1版本的照片频道移除了MP3文件的播放支持并替换为了[[進階音訊編碼|AAC]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://wii.nintendo.com/photo_channel.jsp |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071213040428/http://wii.nintendo.com/photo_channel.jsp |archivedate=2007-12-13 |title=Wii (photo channel) |publisher=任天堂 |accessdate=2007-12-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2008年10月的任天堂秋季新闻发布会，岩田聪公布Wii用户将可以把WiiWare和Virtual Console内容直接下载到下载到SD卡的选项。并称该选项是“解决主机内部储存空间不足的问题”的替代方案。该公告称，该其将于2009年春季在日本上市；<ref>{{cite web|last=Plunkett|first=Luke|url=http://kotaku.com/5057877/save-wii-games-direct-to-sd-card-starting-spring-2009|title=2008 Nintendo Fall Press Conference: Save Wii Games Direct To SD Card (Starting Spring 2009)|publisher=Kotaku|date=2008-10-02|accessdate=2008-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081005052507/http://kotaku.com/5057877/save-wii-games-direct-to-sd-card-starting-spring-2009|archive-date=2008-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>任天堂在3月25日发布了这一更新。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Fahey|first=Mike|url=https://kotaku.com/5183763/wii-system-update-adds-play-from-sd-card-support|title=Wii System Update Adds Play From SD Card Support|work=Kotaku|date=2009-03-25|access-date=2018-11-30|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130113155/https://kotaku.com/5183763/wii-system-update-adds-play-from-sd-card-support|archive-date=2018-11-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>除了之前宣布的功能，这个更新还允许用户直接从SD卡玩游戏。实际上，所有频道的数据还是被复制到了Wii主机中知道玩家手动移除频道。2.0更新后Wii允许频道数据存储在SD卡上，但必须由玩家手动选择复制。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.geek.com/games/nintendo-wii-now-plays-games-directly-from-sd-cards-725431/|title=Nintendo Wii now plays games directly from SD cards - Geek.com|date=2009-03-25|work=Geek.com|access-date=2018-11-30|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130120037/https://www.geek.com/games/nintendo-wii-now-plays-games-directly-from-sd-cards-725431/|archive-date=2018-11-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>更新也添加了对最大容量为32GB的[[Secure_Digital|SDHC]]卡的支持。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Lindemann|first=Jon|url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/18036/the-wii-sd-card-menu-a-walkthrough|title=The Wii SD Card Menu: A Walkthrough - News|website=Nintendo World Report|date=2009-03-05|access-date=2018-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130113032/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/18036/the-wii-sd-card-menu-a-walkthrough|archive-date=2018-11-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===技术参数===
任天堂几乎没有公布多少的Wii系统的技术细节，但一些关键细节后来被被媒体泄露。虽然这些报道都没有经过官方证实，但它们通常都表明这款游戏机是[[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]架构的扩展（或升级）。具体来说，分析报告显示，Wii的性能大约是GameCube的1.5到2倍。<ref name="Wii: The Total Story">{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/launchguide/hardware1.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061218073811/http://wii.ign.com/launchguide/hardware1.html|archivedate=2006-12-18|title=Wii: The Total Story|accessdate=2006-11-20|website=IGN|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="IGN Wii FAQs">{{cite web|last=Casamassina|first=Matt|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/733/733464p7.html|title=IGN's Nintendo Wii FAQ|website=IGN|date=2006-09-19|accessdate=2006-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061031001548/http://wii.ign.com/articles/733/733464p7.html|archive-date=2006-10-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>根据硬件规格，Wii被认为是这一代主要家用游戏机中性能最弱的。<ref name=NYTWii>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/11/24/arts/24wii.html|title=Getting Everybody Back in the Game|first=Seth|last=Schiesel|newspaper=New York Times|date=2006-11-24|accessdate=2012-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130502100842/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/11/24/arts/24wii.html|archive-date=2013-05-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{Col-begin}}

{{Col-2}}

'''处理器：'''
* [[中央处理器|CPU]]：基于[[PowerPC|PowerPC]]的[[Broadway_(微处理器)|Broadway]]处理器，采用[[90纳米制程|90纳米制程]] [[SOI|SOI]] [[互補式金屬氧化物半導體|CMOS]]技术及工艺，据报道{{Ref|clock|†}}运行于729 [[赫兹|MHz]]频率<ref name="IGNTech">{{cite web|title=IGN: Revolution's Horsepower|date=2006-03-29|website=IGN|accessdate=2006-12-23|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/699/699118p1.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522074334/http://wii.ign.com/articles/699/699118p1.html|archive-date=2011-05-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
* [[圖形處理器|GPU]]：[[冶天科技|冶天科技]] {{tsl|en|Hollywood (graphics chip)||Hollywood}}图形处理器，采用90纳米制程 CMOS技术及工艺，<ref name="hard_japan">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/n10/e3_2006/wii/index.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060615131048/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/n10/e3_2006/wii/index.html|archivedate=2006-06-15|title=Wiiの概要 (Wii本体)|work=E3 2006|publisher=Nintendo|accessdate=2006-05-22|language=ja|dead-url=no}}</ref>据报道{{Ref|clock|†}}运行于243 [[赫兹|MHz]]频率<ref name="IGNTech" />

<small>{{note|clock|†}}没有任何一个[[时钟频率|时钟频率]]被[[任天堂|任天堂]]、[[IBM|IBM]]或[[冶天科技|冶天科技]]官方确认。</small>

'''存储器：'''
* 88 [[百萬位元組|MB]][[電腦數據存貯器|主运行内存]]（24 MB 内置于显示处理器的{{tsl|en|1T-SRAM||1T-SRAM}}，64 MB外置[[GDDR3|GDDR3]] SDRAM）<ref name="TechOnWii">{{cite web|title=PS3 VS Wii, Comparisons of Core LSI Chip Areas|date=2006-11-27|publisher=TechOn!|accessdate=2006-12-15|url=http://techon.nikkeibp.co.jp/english/NEWS_EN/20061127/124495/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070103123552/http://techon.nikkeibp.co.jp/english/NEWS_EN/20061127/124495/|archive-date=2007-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 3 MB嵌入式图形处理器{{tsl|en|texture memory||材质内存}}和[[帧缓冲器|帧缓冲器]]

'''端口和外围功能：'''
* 最多连接16个Wii遥控器（10个于标准模式，6个于一次性模式<ref>Wii操作手册：系统设定，第28页。</ref>通过[[藍牙|藍牙]]连接）
* 任天堂GameCube控制器接口（4）
* 任天堂GameCube记忆卡插槽（2）
* [[Secure_Digital|SD]]卡插槽（截至系统版本4.0支持[[Secure_Digital|SDHC]]卡）
* [[USB|USB]] 2.0 接口（2）
* 感应条电源口
* 位于Wii遥控器底部的附件插槽
* USB键盘用于于留言板，Wii商店和互联网频道输入信息（需要系统版本3.0和3.1）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/wii/what/faq#section8_sub7|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080312043408/http://www.nintendo.com/wii/what/faq#section8_sub7|archivedate=2008-03-12|title=Wii — Frequently Asked Questions|accessdate=2008-03-31|publisher=Nintendo|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* [[三美電機|三美電機]] DWM-W004 WiFi 802.11b/g 无线网络模组<ref name="IGN Wii FAQ">{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/733/733464p8.html|title=IGN's Nintendo Wii FAQ|accessdate=2007-01-25|last=Casamassina|first=Matt|authorlink=Matt Casamassina|date=2006-09-20|website=IGN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100502055212/http://wii.ign.com/articles/733/733464p8.html|archive-date=2010-05-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
* 支持可选的[[USB_Power_Delivery|USB]] 2.0转[[以太网|以太]][[局域网|局域网]]转换器
* [[Wii#视频|“AV Multi Out”接口]]

'''内置内容评级系统：'''
* [[英國電影分級委員會|英國電影分級委員會]]（BBFC）、[[電腦娛樂分級機構|電腦娛樂分級機構]]（CERO）、[[娛樂軟件分級委員會|娛樂軟件分級委員會]]（ESRB）、Australian Classification Board（{{tsl|en|Australian Classification Board||ACB}}）、Office of Film and Literature Classification （新西兰）（{{tsl|en|Office of Film and Literature Classification (New Zealand)||OFLC}}）、[[泛歐遊戲資訊組織|泛歐遊戲資訊組織]]（PEGI）、[[德國娛樂軟件檢驗局|德國娛樂軟件檢驗局]]（USK）

{{Col-2}}
[[File:broadwaycpu.JPG|thumb]] 运行处理器|alt=正方形处理芯片]]
[[File:Hollywood_gpu.png|thumb]]
'''存储:'''
* 512 MB内置NAND[[闪存|闪存]]
* 可通过[[Secure_Digital|SD]]和[[Secure_Digital|SDHC]]卡扩展储存（最大32 GB）
* 任天堂GameCube记忆卡（GameCube游戏存档时强制需要）
* 吸入式光盘驱动器，兼容8厘米任天堂GameCube游戏光盘和12厘米Wii光盘
* Macronix {{tsl|en|Mask ROM||Mask ROM}}<ref name="Macronix">{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/719/719299p1.html|title=Macronix Supplies Wii|accessdate=2006-07-18|last=Casamassina|first=Matt|authorlink=Matt Casamassina|date=2006-07-17|website=IGN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522075927/http://wii.ign.com/articles/719/719299p1.html|archive-date=2011-05-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

'''{{anchor|视频}}视频：'''
* 独有“AV Multi Out”接口：支持[[AV端子|复合视频]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/wii/en_na/setupAV.jsp|title=Nintendo Support: Connecting the Wii AV Cables|accessdate=2010-02-28|publisher=Nintendo|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100305230952/http://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/wii/en_na/setupAV.jsp|archive-date=2010-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[色差端子|YP<sub>B</sub>P<sub>R</sub>]][[色差端子|复合视频]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/wii/en_na/setupComponents.jsp|title=Nintendo Support: About Component Video|accessdate=2010-02-28|publisher=Nintendo|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100310155310/http://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/wii/en_na/setupComponents.jsp|archive-date=2010-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[S-端子|S-端子]]（仅限[[NTSC制式|NTSC制式]]机型）<ref>{{cite web|url= http://wii.nintendo.com/console.jsp|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080208235448/http://wii.nintendo.com/console.jsp|archivedate= 2008-02-08|title= What is Wii?|accessdate= 2007-09-18|publisher= Nintendo|dead-url= no}}</ref>和[[色差端子|RGB]] {{tsl|en|SCART||SCART}}（仅限[[PAL制式|PAL制式]]机型）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Wii/Accessories/Accessories-Wii-Nintendo-UK-626430.html|title=Nintendo UK: Wii Accessories|accessdate=2014-08-09|publisher=Nintendo}}</ref>
* [[480p|480p]]（[[PAL制式|PAL]]/[[NTSC制式|NTSC]]）、[[480i|480i]]（PAL/NTSC）或[[576i|576i]]（PAL），标准4:3或[[長寬比_(影像)|16:9]]{{tsl|en|anamorphic widescreen||变形宽屏幕}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3154939|archive-url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20160522225319/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3154939|archive-date=2016-05-22|title=Wii Get It Now: Technical Specs|website=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|first=Amy|last=McDonough|date=2006-11-06|accessdate=2008-09-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

'''音频：'''
* 双声道音频，支援{{tsl|en|Pro Logic II||Dolby Pro Logic II}}<ref name="Dolby Pro Logic II">{{cite press release|title=Dolby Technology to Power the Sound of the Wii Console|publisher=Dolby Laboratories|date=2006-09-21|url=http://investor.dolby.com/ReleaseDetail.cfm?ReleaseID=211978|accessdate=2006-09-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061020135248/http://investor.dolby.com/ReleaseDetail.cfm?ReleaseID=211978|archivedate=2006-10-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
* 遥控器内置单声道扬声器
* 音频[[数字信号处理器|数字信号处理器]]

'''电源消耗：'''
* 主机开启时：18[[瓦特|瓦特]]<ref name="Consume">{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoreware.net/reviews/review-356-2.htm|title=Xbox 360 vs PS3 (and Wii) - Power Consumption Report|accessdate=2007-11-17|publisher=Hardcoreware.net|first=Carl|last=Nelson|date=2007-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071127022736/http://www.hardcoreware.net/reviews/review-356-2.htm|archive-date=2007-11-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 待机并连接[[WiiConnect24|WiiConnect24]]时：9.6瓦特<ref name="Consume"/>
* 待机时：1.3瓦特<ref name="Consume"/>

