===技术问题===
第一个Wii系统软件更新通过WiiConnect24发布，造成了少数首发机型[[砖_(电子设备)|完全无法使用]]。迫使用户将机器寄送到[[任天堂|任天堂]]进行维修（如果用户想要保留他们的游戏存档数据）或进行免费更换。<ref name="Wii Firmware down">{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=149572|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080616142826/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=149572|archivedate=2008-06-16|title=Wii Connect 24 Kills Wiis|publisher=[[电脑与电子游戏|电脑与电子游戏]]|date=2006-11-21|first=Mike|last=Jackson|accessdate=2008-09-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>

随着双层Wii光盘的发布，美国任天堂公司表示，一些Wii机器可能由于激光镜头被污染而难以读取高密度光盘。任天堂为这一问题发售了激光镜头清洗工具并提供免费的游戏机维修服务。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/repair/repair_form_us_ssbb.jsp|title=Repair Form for U.S. Residents|accessdate=2008-03-11|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223052430/http://www.nintendo.com/consumer/repair/repair_form_us_ssbb.jsp|archive-date=2008-12-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BRAWLERROS">{{cite web|url=http://gonintendo.com/?p=40081|title=Brawl disc read errors return, but this time it's Mario Kart|publisher=GoNintendo|date=2008-04-11|accessdate=2008-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080623203109/http://gonintendo.com/?p=40081|archive-date=2008-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Wii遥控器可能会失去与已配对的Wii系统的连接，需要重新设置和同步。任天堂的支持网站为这一问题提供了故障排除说明。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.nintendo.com/|title=Nintendo support website|publisher=Nintendo|access-date=2020-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080606225659/http://www.support.nintendo.com/|archive-date=2008-06-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==机能==
<!--{{See also|Wii system software}}-->
主机通过其硬件和[[韌體|固件]]为用户提供了许多功能，硬件上Wii能连接许多第三方外设配件，固件上用户能通过[[WiiConnect24|WiiConnect24]]来使用和接收到许多服务及更新。<!--
The latest firmware version for the Wii system is 2.2U. In order to use Channels requiring Internet access, a firmware update is required.<ref name="IGN Firmware">{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/745/745341p1.html|title=IGN: Wii Channels to Require Upgrade|accessdate=2006-10-12|date=2006-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061217003751/http://wii.ign.com/articles/745/745341p1.html|archive-date=2006-12-17}}</ref> -->

===Wii菜单===
<!--[[File:Wiimen.png|thumb]]|alt=Wii菜单的截图]]-->

Wii菜单界面的设计模仿了[[电视频道|电视频道]]的风格。许多不同的频道以方格排列在画面中，用户使用[[Wii遥控器|Wii遥控器]]的指点功能进行选择。除了光盘频道外，其他所有的频道都可以通过同时按下控制器上的A和B按钮来“抓住”频道并移动其在画面方格中的位置。Wii总共有6个主要的频道：光盘频道、Mii频道、照片频道、Wii商店频道、[[Wii頻道#天氣頻道|天气预报频道]]以及[[Wii頻道#新聞頻道|新闻频道]]。最后两个频道在Wii首发时尚无法使用，并在后期通过系统更新进行启用。自2008年10月后，Wii + 网络视频频道开始预装在所有的Wii机器中。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/wii/en_na/channelsWiiInternetVideo.jsp|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225181747/https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/wii/en_na/channelsWiiInternetVideo.jsp|archive-date=2009-02-25|title={{!}} Nintendo - Customer Service {{!}} Wii - Wii + Internet Channel Video|date=2009-02-25|access-date=2018-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>其他附加频道，如[[WiiWare|WiiWare]]和[[Virtual_Console|Virtual Console]]游戏，可以通过[[Wii商店频道|Wii商店频道]]的进行下载；例如[[Wii頻道#大家的投票頻道|大家的投票频道]]、[[Wii頻道#互联网频道|互联网频道]]、{{tsl|en|Check Mii Out Channel||Check Mii Out频道}}以及[[Wii頻道#大家的任天堂頻道|大家的任天堂频道]]。

===向下兼容===
<!-- - Wii Download Games Should not Be Mixed With Launch Titles - -->
[[File:Wii-gamecube-compatibility.jpg|thumb]]记忆卡和控制器|alt=Wii主机上连接着黑色GameCube控制器以及黑色GameCube记忆卡]]
Wii主机最初就设计为[[向下兼容|向下兼容]][[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]软件、任天堂GameCube记忆卡以及任天堂GameCube控制器。软件兼容是通过吸入式光驱支持[[任天堂光盘#任天堂GameCube遊戲光碟|任天堂GameCube游戏光碟]]来实现的。但是，Wii的重新设计机型RVL-101和Wii Mini不支持向下兼容功能。<ref name="Wii2.0" /><ref name="EurogamerReview" />

运行GameCube光盘时的Wii主机的机能会有所限制，要游玩GameCube游戏，用户必须拥有GameCube控制器。如果用户想要存储游戏进度及内容，用户必须使用GameCube记忆卡；Wii内部闪存无法存储GameCube游戏存档文件。<ref name=CNETAcc>{{cite web|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-9663541-1.html|title=Must-have Nintendo Wii accessories|first=John P.|last=Falcone|date=2006-11-16|accessdate=2012-09-13|website=CNET|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307065021/http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-9663541-1.html|archive-date=2012-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外，向下兼容功能在某些方面也会有所限制。例如，部分GameCube游戏的在线或局域网多人游戏功能无法在Wii上使用，因为Wii并没有用于连接{{tsl|en|Nintendo GameCube Broadband Adapter and Modem Adapter||任天堂GameCube宽带和调制解调器转接器}}的串行连接口。<ref name=CNETFAQ>{{cite web|url=http://reviews.cnet.com/4520-10166_7-6676348-1.html|title=Which of my older video games will work on the new consoles?|date=2006-12-12|first=John|last=Falcone|website=CNET|accessdate=2012-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007005205/http://reviews.cnet.com/4520-10166_7-6676348-1.html|archive-date=2012-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===任天堂DS连接能力===
Wii系统可以不使用任何外部设备来与[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]进行无线连接。这个功能能让玩家使用任天堂DS的麦克风和[[觸控式螢幕|觸控式螢幕]]来控制Wii游戏。第一个使用这个功能的Wii游戏是《[[精靈寶可夢戰鬥革命|精靈寶可夢戰鬥革命]]》：玩家可以使用正在运行[[精靈寶可夢_鑽石·珍珠|《精靈寶可夢 鑽石》或《精靈寶可夢 珍珠》]]游戏的任天堂DS当作控制器来操控Wii进行游玩。<ref name="connectivity returns">{{cite web|last=Gantayat|first=Anoop|date=2006-06-07|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/711/711657p1.html|title=Connectivity Returns|website=IGN|accessdate=2006-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204204716/http://wii.ign.com/articles/711/711657p1.html|archive-date=2012-02-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>游戏《[[最终幻想水晶编年史_时之回声|最终幻想水晶编年史 时之回声]]》同时在Wii和任天堂DS上推出，其也支持连接功能，使玩家在两个游戏上的进度相同。任天堂后来发布了[[Wii頻道#大家的任天堂頻道|大家的任天堂频道]]，其能使玩家下载[[游戏演示|游戏演示]]或其他附加数据到任天堂DS上，与{{tsl|en|DS Download Station||DS下载站}}功能类似。<ref name="Iwata Tech-On 3">{{cite web|first=Naoki|last=Asami|author2=Hiroki Yomogita|date=2006-05-25|url=http://techon.nikkeibp.co.jp/english/NEWS_EN/20060525/117498/?P=3|title=Regaining what we have lost: Nintendo CEO Iwata's Ambitions for the "Wii"|work=Tech-On!|page=3|publisher=Nikkei Business Publications|accessdate=2006-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060614143115/http://techon.nikkeibp.co.jp/english/NEWS_EN/20060525/117498/?P=3|archive-date=2006-06-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii也能对DS游戏进行扩展。<ref name="connectivity returns" />

===在线能力===
{{Main|任天堂Wi-Fi连接|Wii頻道#频道|Wii頻道#互联网频道}}

Wii主机可以通过其内置的[[IEEE_802.11|802.11b]]/[[IEEE_802.11|g]] WiFi或外置的USB转以太网转接器连接到互联网；这两个方法都可以让玩家连接到[[任天堂Wi-Fi连接|任天堂Wi-Fi连接]]服务。<ref name="Wii: The Total Story" />这个服务为玩家提供了许多功能，如[[Virtual_Console|Virtual Console]]，[[WiiConnect24|WiiConnect24]]，[[Wii頻道#互联网频道|互联网频道]]，[[Wii頻道#天氣頻道|天气预报频道]]、[[Wii頻道#大家的投票頻道|大家的投票频道]]、[[Wii頻道#新聞頻道|新闻频道]]和{{tsl|en|Check Mii Out Channel||Check Mii Out频道}}。Wii也支持自己建立无线[[局域网|局域网]]来与其他Wii连接和通信，使玩家能在本地无线多人在不同的电视上游玩游戏，《{{tsl|en|Battalion Wars 2|军团战争2}}》是第一个使用这个功能的游戏，其能使用多台电视机和Wii进行不分屏的多人游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/727/727651p1.html|title=Battalion Wars 2 Hands On|website=IGN|first=Mario|last=Kablau|date=2006-08-23|accessdate=2007-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060902202730/http://wii.ign.com/articles/727/727651p1.html|archive-date=2006-09-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

====影音功能====
2008年4月9日，[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]宣布其在线服务[[BBC_iPlayer|BBC iPlayer]]将会通过[[Wii頻道#互联网频道|互联网频道]]在Wii上可用；但是部分用户在使用这项功能时遇到了困难。2009年11月18日，英国广播公司在Wii上推出了BBC iPlayer频道，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/8357777.stm|title=BBC iPlayer launches Wii channel|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2009-12-26|date=2009-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007183338/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/8357777.stm|archive-date=2018-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/bbcinternet/2009/11/the_new_iplayer_on_the_nintend.html|title=The new iPlayer on the Nintendo Wii|publisher=BBC|date=2009-11-13|accessdate=2009-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091227123811/http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/bbcinternet/2009/11/the_new_iplayer_on_the_nintend.html|archive-date=2009-12-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>其可以从[[Wii商店频道|Wii商店频道]]上免费下载；<ref>{{cite web|url=http://iplayerhelp.external.bbc.co.uk/help/playing_tv_progs/nintendo_Wii|title=Can I access BBC iPlayer on my Nintendo Wii game system?|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2010-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100925064941/http://iplayerhelp.external.bbc.co.uk/help/playing_tv_progs/nintendo_Wii|archive-date=2010-09-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>这项服务于2017年初停止运行。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2016/09/bbc_iplayer_app_to_end_service_on_wii_u_in_early_2017|title=BBC iPlayer App to End Service on Wii U in Early 2017|last=Whitehead|first=Thomas|work=Nintendo Life|date=2016-09-30|access-date=2018-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180819083521/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2016/09/bbc_iplayer_app_to_end_service_on_wii_u_in_early_2017|archive-date=2018-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[Netflix|Netflix]]于2010年10月18日在加拿大和美国在[[Wii商店频道|Wii商店频道]]上发布了Netflix频道。<ref name="Netflix-Nodisc">{{cite news |author=Devindra Hardawar |url=https://venturebeat.com/2010/10/18/netflix-streaming-video-now-disc-free-on-the-nintendo-wii/ |title=Netflix streaming video now disc-free on the Nintendo Wii |work=VentureBeat |date=2010-10-18 |accessdate=2010-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101120171407/http://venturebeat.com/2010/10/18/netflix-streaming-video-now-disc-free-on-the-nintendo-wii/ |archive-date=2010-11-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>根据一份来自[[尼爾森NV|尼爾森NV]]的调查报告，截至2011年7月，有25%的Netflix订阅者使用Wii上的Netflix频道来使用Netflix服务。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blog.nielsen.com/nielsenwire/online_mobile/what-netflix-and-hulu-users-are-watching-and-how/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110729024009/http://blog.nielsen.com/nielsenwire/online_mobile/what-netflix-and-hulu-users-are-watching-and-how/|archive-date=2011-07-29|title=What Netflix and Hulu Users are Watching… and How {{!}} Nielsen Wire|date=2011-07-29|access-date=2018-08-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

[[Hulu|Hulu]]于2011年10月宣布他们将会在Wii和[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]上发布其自己的[[流媒体|流媒体服务]]Hulu Plus。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.engadget.com/2011/10/21/hulu-plus-coming-to-3ds-and-wii-handheld-getting-3d-video-captu/|title=Hulu Plus coming to 3DS and Wii, handheld getting 3D video capture|work=Engadget|date=2011-10-21|access-date=2018-08-07|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807033024/https://www.engadget.com/2011/10/21/hulu-plus-coming-to-3ds-and-wii-handheld-getting-3d-video-captu/|archive-date=2018-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>Hulu Plus于2012年2月16日在Wii上作为可免费下载的频道发布。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/2012/2/16/2802355/hulu-plus-wii-available|title=Hulu Plus for Wii available for download now|work=The Verge|date=2012-02-16|access-date=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807034400/https://www.theverge.com/2012/2/16/2802355/hulu-plus-wii-available|archive-date=2018-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[YouTube|YouTube]]在2012年12月15日于美国在Wii上发布了其可下载频道、<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://wii.mmgn.com/News/youtube-finally-makes-it-to-the-wii-1340|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121120040550/http://wii.mmgn.com/News/youtube-finally-makes-it-to-the-wii-1340|archive-date=2012-11-20|title=YouTube finally makes it to the Wii - Wii News {{!}} MMGN Australia|date=2012-11-20|access-date=2018-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii上的YouTube频道于2017年6月28日停止运行，这是YouTube计划淘汰旧设备的一部分。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://en-americas-support.nintendo.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/26400/p/604|title=YouTube for Wii Service Has Ended {{!}} Wii & Wii mini {{!}} Nintendo Support|website=en-americas-support.nintendo.com|language=en-US|access-date=2018-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404212559/https://en-americas-support.nintendo.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/26400/p/604|archive-date=2019-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[亞馬遜影片|亞馬遜影片]]，[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]的流媒体服务，于2013年1月14日在Wii上以可下载频道的方式发布。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-set-up-amazon-instant-video-on-the-nintendo-wii/|title=How to set up Amazon Instant Video on the Nintendo Wii|date=2013-01-15|work=CNET|access-date=2018-08-07|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807063412/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/how-to-set-up-amazon-instant-video-on-the-nintendo-wii/|archive-date=2018-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://phx.corporate-ir.net/phoenix.zhtml?c=176060&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1774342&highlight=|title=Amazon - Press Room - Press Release|website=phx.corporate-ir.net|access-date=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404212532/http://phx.corporate-ir.net/phoenix.zhtml?c=176060&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1774342&highlight=|archive-date=2019-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]，一个[[日本动画|日本动画]]流媒体播放服务，于2015年10月15日以可下载频道的方式在Wii上发布。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2015/10/15-1/crunchyroll-app-now-available-on-nintendo-wii|title=Crunchyroll App Now Available on Nintendo Wii|work=Crunchyroll|date=2015-10-16|access-date=2018-08-07|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016130447/http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2015/10/15-1/crunchyroll-app-now-available-on-nintendo-wii|archive-date=2015-10-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年，Netflix宣布任天堂将于2019年1月30日关闭Wii的视频流媒体服务的支持，包括Netflix。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://devices.netflix.com/en/game-consoles/wii/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109093106/https://devices.netflix.com/en/game-consoles/wii/|archive-date=2018-11-09|title=Wii|work=Netflix|date=2018-11-09|access-date=2018-11-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===家长控制===
Wii支持{{tsl|en|parental controls||家长控制}}，其被用于防止年轻用户游玩拥有不适合其年龄段的内容的游戏。当用户尝试打开Wii或[[Virtual_Console|Virtual Console]]游戏时，主机会读取存储在游戏数据中的分级数据，如果分级数据大于系统中设定的年龄等级，游戏将停止加载，直到玩家输入家长控制密码。家长控制功能也可以限制互联网访问功能，其能屏蔽[[Wii頻道#互联网频道|互联网频道]]和系统更新功能。因为Wii在运行[[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]游戏时会限制部分Wii机能，家长控制功能不影响任天堂GameCube游戏。<ref name=CNETParent>{{cite magazine|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-9880634-1.html|title=Super-Easy Game Play - Nintendo Wii Reviewi|magazine=PC Magazine|first=Will|last=Greenwald|date=2008-02-29|accessdate=2012-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120810135911/http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-9880634-1.html|archive-date=2012-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

欧洲机型主要使用[[泛歐遊戲資訊組織|泛歐遊戲資訊組織]]（PEGI）分级系统，<ref name="par_pegi">{{cite news|url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/newsArt.cfm?artid=10948|title=Revolution To Feature Parental Controls|publisher=Nintendo World Report|date=2005-11-16|accessdate=2008-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080617024654/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/newsArt.cfm?artid=10948|archive-date=2008-06-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>北美机型主要使用[[娛樂軟件分級委員會|娛樂軟件分級委員會]]（ESRB）分级系统。<ref name="par_esrb">{{cite press release|url=https://www.nintendo.com/newsarticle?articleid=z5UnNGZpQKWULzG0z8R501PA5IHoNPr2|title=Nintendo Announces Play Control System For Next Hardware|publisher=Nintendo|date=2005-11-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070213012428/http://www.nintendo.com/newsarticle?articleid=z5UnNGZpQKWULzG0z8R501PA5IHoNPr2|archivedate=2007-02-13|access-date=2020-01-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii支持许多分级系统，例如在日本使用的[[電腦娛樂分級機構|電腦娛樂分級機構]]（CERO）系统，在德国使用的[[德國娛樂軟件檢驗局|德國娛樂軟件檢驗局]]（USK）系统，在英国使用的使用[[泛歐遊戲資訊組織|泛歐遊戲資訊組織]]（PEGI）和[[英國電影分級委員會|英國電影分級委員會]]（BBFC）系统，在澳大利亚使用的{{tsl|en|Australian Classification Board}}（ACB）系统和在新西兰使用的{{tsl|en|Office of Film and Literature Classification (New Zealand)||Office of Film and Literature Classification}}（OFLC）系统。自制软件开发者也反向工程了任天堂的家长控制功能，创建了能重置遗忘的家长控制密码的代码。<ref>{{cite web |author=marcan |url=http://hackmii.com/2008/05/parental-controls/ |title=Parental Controls |publisher=HackmMii.com |date=2008-05-15 |accessdate=2009-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090224155247/http://hackmii.com/2008/05/parental-controls/ |archive-date=2009-02-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==评价和反应==
Wii得到了普遍的好评。该系统在[[E3电子娱乐展|2006年E3展览]]中也受到了普遍好评。在活动中，任天堂的游戏机赢得了[[游戏评论家奖|游戏评论家奖]]中的的展览最佳和最佳硬件奖。<ref name="E3 Awards">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamecriticsawards.com/2006winners.html|title=2006 Winners|accessdate=2006-08-13|work=Game Critics Awards|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414080540/http://www.gamecriticsawards.com/2006winners.html|archive-date=2016-04-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2006年12月的《[[科技新时代|科技新时代]]》杂志上，Wii获得了家庭娱乐大奖。<ref name="pop-sci-nov06-80">{{Cite journal|title=Best of What's New 2006 - Home Entertainment|journal=[[科技新时代|科技新时代]]|volume=269|issue=6|date=December 2006|pages= 80}}</ref>[[派拉蒙电视网|派拉蒙电视网]]的视频游戏奖提到了Wii的突破性技术。<ref name="Spike TV Award">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/6162929.html? |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070207083115/http://www.gamespot.com/news/6162929.html |archivedate=2007-02-07 |title=Oblivion nabs Spike TV top honors |accessdate=2007-03-10 |website=GameSpot |first=Tim |last=Surette |date=2006-12-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]在“2006年度最佳和最差硬件”评选中，选择了Wii作为最佳硬件。<ref name="Gamespot Award">{{cite web|url= http://www.gamespot.com/special_features/bestof2006/achievement/index.html?page=21|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070203011403/http://www.gamespot.com/special_features/bestof2006/achievement/index.html?page=21|archivedate= 2007-02-03|title= GameSpot Best Games and Worst Games of 2006|accessdate= 2007-03-10|website= GameSpot|dead-url= no}}</ref>该系统还被《[[PC_World|PC World]]》杂志选为年度20个最具创新力的产品之一。<ref name="PC World Award">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/128176-2/the_20_most_innovative_products_of_the_year.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080118042456/http://www.pcworld.com/article/id%2C128176-page%2C2-c%2Celectronics/article.html |archivedate=2008-01-18 |title=The 20 Most Innovative Products of the Year |accessdate=2007-03-10 |magazine=[[PC_World|PC World]] |date=2006-12-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>这款游戏机在2007年的[[金摇杆奖|金摇杆奖]]上获得了年度创新奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/28700/Gears-of-War-swoops-Golden-Joysticks|title=Gears of War scoops Golden Joysticks|first=Ben|last=Parfitt|publisher=mcvuk.com|date=2007-10-26|accessdate=2007-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071028103626/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/28700/Gears-of-War-swoops-Golden-Joysticks|archive-date=2007-10-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>在电子游戏与平台的开发与实现的工程与技术领域，任天堂获得了美国国家电视艺术与科学学院颁发的游戏控制器创新艾美奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emmyonline.org/mediacenter/tech_2k7_winners.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509070210/http://www.emmyonline.org/mediacenter/tech_2k7_winners.html|archivedate=2008-05-09|title=Winners of 59th Technology & Engineering Emmy Awards|date=2008-01-08|accessdate=2008-01-14|website=emmyonline.org|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2009年，IGN将Wii评为史上最伟大的游戏机第十位（总共25位）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/top-25-consoles/10.html |title=Nintendo Wii is number 10 |website=IGN |accessdate=2010-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203105301/http://www.ign.com/top-25-consoles/10.html |archive-date=2010-12-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Wii的成功让第三方开发者措手不及，许多开发者为他们早期游戏的质量道歉。在接受德国新闻杂志《[[明镜|明镜]]》采访时，[[育碧|育碧]]的伊夫·吉列莫特和阿兰·科雷承认，他们匆忙推出自己的游戏是个错误，他们承诺将更严肃地对待未来的项目。<ref>{{cite web|last=Görig|first=Carsten|newspaper=[[明镜|明镜]]|title=Spieler verzweifelt gesucht|date=2007-05-30|url=http://www.spiegel.de/netzwelt/spielzeug/0,1518,485385,00.html|language=de|accessdate=2007-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129202504/http://www.spiegel.de/netzwelt/spielzeug/0,1518,485385,00.html|archive-date=2012-01-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>仅为GameCube发布过几款游戏的[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]]也改变了对任天堂的态度，将Wii放在了更重要的位置。<ref>{{cite web|last=Seff|first=Micah|website=IGN|title=Take-Two Grows Hungry for Wii|date=2007-04-10|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/779/779642p1.html|accessdate=2007-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070606151413/http://wii.ign.com/articles/779/779642p1.html|archive-date=2007-06-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

与此同时，对Wii遥控器和Wii硬件规格的批评也浮出了水面。GameSpot前编辑、Giantbomb.com网站创始人{{tsl|en|Jeff Gerstmann|杰夫·格斯特曼}}表示，遥控器的扬声器的声音质量很低，<ref name="Tinny Speaker">{{cite web|last=Gerstmann|first=Jeff|date=2006-11-17|url=http://www.gamespot.com/wii/action/thelegendofzelda/review.html|title=The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2007-03-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070303150330/http://www.gamespot.com/wii/action/thelegendofzelda/review.html|archivedate=2007-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>而{{tsl|en|Factor 5}}的总裁朱利安·埃格布雷希特则批评说，Wii的音频硬件不符合这一代游戏机的标准。<ref name="Rock You">{{cite web|last= Radd|first= David|title= Wii Won't Rock You|date= 2006-11-17|publisher= GameDaily.biz|accessdate= 2007-01-31|url= http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/features/opinion-wii-wont-rock-you/69717/?biz=1|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20071211233003/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/features/opinion-wii-wont-rock-you/69717/?biz=1|archivedate= 2007-12-11|dead-url= no}}</ref>总部位于英国的开发商[[Crytek_UK|Free Radical Design]]表示，Wii的硬件缺乏运行其计划在其他第七代游戏机上发布的游戏所需的能力。<ref name="Free Radical">{{cite web|url=http://www.frd.co.uk/faq.php?id=3#faq_3|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071214224330/http://www.frd.co.uk/faq.php?id=3#faq_3|archivedate=2007-12-14|title=Free Radical Design FAQ|publisher=frd.co.uk|accessdate=2007-03-08|dead-url=no}}</ref> Wii的网络连接能力也受到了批评；[[IGN|IGN]]的{{tsl|en|Matt Casamassina|马特·卡萨马西纳}}将Wii和[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]比较时称Wii的网络连接功能“完全不直观”。<ref>{{cite web|last= Casamassina|first= Matt|title= N-Query|date= 2007-01-24|publisher= [[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate= 2007-01-27|url= http://wii.ign.com/mail/2007-01-24.html|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070303144047/http://wii.ign.com/mail/2007-01-24.html|archivedate= 2007-03-03|dead-url= yes}}</ref>

游戏设计师和《模拟人生系列》的创始人[[威爾·萊特|威爾·萊特]]在第七代游戏机的背景下分享了他对Wii的看法：“我认为我目前看见的唯一一个下一世代游戏机只有Wii；PS3和Xbox 360感觉只是其上一代的性能加强版本而已，游戏也几乎都是同样的游戏，只是做了些小小的改进罢了。但Wii给人的感觉是一个巨大的飞跃，不是因为它的画面性能更强大，而是它完全触及到了一个完全不同的人群。”<ref name="wii_next_gen">{{cite web|website=Guardian Unlimited|date=2007-10-26|title=Q&A: Will Wright, creator of the Sims|author=Johnson, Bobbie|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2007/oct/26/willwright|accessdate=2008-09-25|location=London|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013050940/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2007/oct/26/willwright|archive-date=2013-10-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>

游玩Wii被认为比游玩其他游戏机更需要体力。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB116441076273232312|title=A Wii Workout: When Videogames Hurt|first=Jamin|last=Warren|date=2006-11-25|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2008-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717024827/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB116441076273232312|archive-date=2017-07-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>一些Wii玩家在游玩后患上了[[肱骨外上髁炎|肱骨外上髁炎]]，这被玩家们称为被称为“Wiiitis”。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/technologyNews/idUSN0616721120070606|title=If it's not tennis elbow, it may be "Wiiitis"|date=2007-06-06|work=Reuters|accessdate=2008-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080307173333/http://www.reuters.com/article/technologyNews/idUSN0616721120070606|archive-date=2008-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[英國醫學期刊|英國醫學期刊]]》发表的一项研究称，Wii玩家比久坐不动的电脑游戏玩家消耗更多的能量。虽然这种能量的增加可能有利于体重的控制，但它并不能完全代替日常锻炼。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/7155342.stm|title=Wii players need to exercise too|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞網|英國廣播公司新聞網]]|date=2007-12-21|accessdate=2008-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201035153/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/7155342.stm|archive-date=2008-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国物理治疗协会的期刊《物理治疗》上发表了一项案例研究，研究重点是让一名[[腦性麻痺|腦性麻痺]]青少年使用Wii进行康复治疗；其被认为是第一个被发表的研究证明了游戏系统的使用有益于物理疗法。研究人员表示，该系统通过同时使用{{tsl|en|gaming rehabilitation||游戏康复}}努力来补充传统技术。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://newswise.com/articles/view/544616/ |title=Research Shows Rehabilitation Benefits of Using Nintendo Wii |author=Schectman, Joel |date=2008-09-23 |newspaper=Newswise |accessdate=2008-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080929202605/http://www.newswise.com/articles/view/544616/ |archive-date=2008-09-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年5月，{{tsl|en|American Heart Association||美国心脏协会}}支持Wii，鼓励[[坐式生活型態|久坐不动的人]]迈出健身的第一步。Wii及其两款需要活跃运动的游戏《[[Wii_Fit_Plus|Wii Fit Plus]]》和《[[Wii運動_度假勝地|Wii運動 度假勝地]]》被打上了“AHA Heart”的标志。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://thedailynewsonline.com/lifestyles/features/article_27fe3fe5-44c0-54e0-b832-774f692c78b4.html |title=Heart group backs Wii video game console in obesity campaign |author=Schectman, Joel |agency=Associated Press |date=2010-05-17 |newspaper=The Daily News (N.Y.) |accessdate=2011-12-28 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120720210916/http://thedailynewsonline.com/lifestyles/features/article_27fe3fe5-44c0-54e0-b832-774f692c78b4.html |archivedate=2012-07-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.activeplaynow.com/ |title=American Heart Association and Nintendo of America Online Information Center |publisher=Activeplaynow.com |date=2010-01-20 |accessdate=2010-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101116100442/http://activeplaynow.com/ |archive-date=2010-11-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2008年，Wii发布2年后，<ref name=IwataAsksWiiU1>{{cite web|title=Iwata Asks: E3 2011 Special Edition|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_special_edition_wii_u_43781_43761.html|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]]|page=1|accessdate=2011-06-09|quote='''Iwata''': I've been looking back at my calendar right before this interview, and I noticed that it's been just about three years since we started having meetings about this.|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204230706/https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Iwata-Asks/Iwata-Asks-E3-2011-Special-Edition-Wii-U/E3-2011-Special-Edition-Wii-U/1-Looking-Beyond-Wii/1-Looking-Beyond-Wii-205181.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>任天堂承认了Wii主机的许多局限性，如主机主要是面向[[休闲游戏|休闲游戏]]而开发的，<ref name=IwataAsksWiiU2>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_special_edition_wii_u_43781_43761.html|title=Iwata Asks: E3 2011 Special Edition|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]]|page=7|accessdate=2011-06-09|quote='''Iwata''': The other things is, shortly after the Wii console was released, people in the gaming media and game enthusiasts started recognizing the Wii as a casual machine aimed toward families, and placed game consoles by Microsoft and Sony in a very similar light with each other, saying these are machines aimed towards those who passionately play games. [...] It was a categorization between games that were aimed towards core, and casual.|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204230706/https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Iwata-Asks/Iwata-Asks-E3-2011-Special-Edition-Wii-U/E3-2011-Special-Edition-Wii-U/1-Looking-Beyond-Wii/1-Looking-Beyond-Wii-205181.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而缺乏对“核心”玩家的关注。<ref name=IwataAsksWiiU3>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_special_edition_wii_u_43781_43761.html|title=Iwata Asks: E3 2011 Special Edition|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]]|page=7|accessdate=2011-06-09|quote='''Iwata''': On the other hand, I certainly do not think that Wii was able to cater to every gamer's needs, so that's also something I wanted to resolve. [...] The keyword for our presentation at this year's E3 is "Deeper and Wider". With Wii U, I would like to offer this proposal with that concept.|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204230706/https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Iwata-Asks/Iwata-Asks-E3-2011-Special-Edition-Wii-U/E3-2011-Special-Edition-Wii-U/1-Looking-Beyond-Wii/1-Looking-Beyond-Wii-205181.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>游戏设计师[[宫本茂|宫本茂]]承认Wii在[[高清电视|高清视频]]输出和网络连接方面的落后使其与其竞争对手[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]和[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]分离。<ref name=IwataAsksWiiU4>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_special_edition_wii_u_43781_43761.html|title=Iwata Asks: E3 2011 Special Edition|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]]|page=7|accessdate=2011-06-09|quote='''Miyamoto''': But one of the key reasons that such things as the core and the casuals exist today is that we decided not to adopt HD on the Wii console. Of course, besides that there are things like issues with the controller and the challenges that it brings, network functionalities and many other things, but I think HD was the biggest factor that everyone was able to clearly understand the difference.|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204230706/https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Iwata-Asks/Iwata-Asks-E3-2011-Special-Edition-Wii-U/E3-2011-Special-Edition-Wii-U/1-Looking-Beyond-Wii/1-Looking-Beyond-Wii-205181.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>宫本茂为Wii不支持高清图像解释称，当时高清电视的用户“还不是特别多，当然我认为五年后任天堂肯定会再出一款支持高清画面的游戏机，但当下人们使用的电视机基本都是非高清的。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/05/11/e3-2006-miyamoto-successor-to-wii-hd|title=E3 2006: Miyamoto: Successor to Wii HD|last=Hatfield|first=Daemon|date=2006-05-11|website=IGN|language=en-US|access-date=2018-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831072233/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/05/11/e3-2006-miyamoto-successor-to-wii-hd|archive-date=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref> 宫本茂在2013年的一次与日本杂志[[4Gamer.net|4Gamer]]的采访中表示他很后悔没有为Wii添加高清图像的支持。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://nintendotoday.com/miyamoto-on-hd-wii/|title=Miyamoto says he wished Nintendo had gone HD with the Wii - NintendoToday|date=2013-07-19|work=NintendoToday|access-date=2018-08-31|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831072132/https://nintendotoday.com/miyamoto-on-hd-wii/|archive-date=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/07/shigeru_miyamoto_wanted_to_go_to_hd_sooner_with_the_wii|title=Shigeru Miyamoto "Wanted to go to HD Sooner" With the Wii|last=Life|first=Nintendo|date=2013-07-19|work=Nintendo Life|access-date=2018-08-31|language=en-GB|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831073522/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/07/shigeru_miyamoto_wanted_to_go_to_hd_sooner_with_the_wii|archive-date=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Frontline工作室的一位高管称主要发行商们对为Wii发行独占游戏十分谨慎，因为他们认为消费者们对第三方公司并不是十分的支持。<ref name="Wary Publishers">{{cite web|last=Martin|first=Matt|title=Publishers wary of creating Nintendo titles, says Wii developer|date=2007-01-24|website=[[Eurogamer|GamesIndustry.biz]]|accessdate=2007-01-27|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/publishers-wary-of-creating-nintendo-titles-says-wii-developer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071211030359/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/content_page.php?aid=22368|archivedate=2007-12-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的编辑杰瑞米·帕里什在他的[[網誌|網誌]]中表示任天堂是他在2007年最大的失望。在谈到缺乏高质量的第三方开发商支持时，他说:“Wii的前景是暗淡的。比任天堂64更糟。比任天堂GameCube更糟糕……由此产生的第三方内容基本上都是廉价的垃圾游戏。”<ref name="JeremyParish2007">{{cite web|last=Parish|first=Jeremy|title=-3 in 2007|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] blog|url=http://www.1up.com/do/blogEntry?bId=8601568&publicUserId=5379721|date=2008-01-29|accessdate=2008-09-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522130049/http://www.1up.com/do/blogEntry?bId=8601568&publicUserId=5379721|archivedate=2011-05-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>《[[环球邮报|环球邮报]]》和《福布斯》指出，Wii与其竞争对手相比，基本没有成功的第三方游戏，其中部分原因是其较弱的机器性能。第三方开发者在开发游戏时一般不会考虑为三款游戏机同时开发游戏，而是选择直接跳过Wii。（“像《[[決勝時刻系列|決勝時刻系列]]》这类风靡一时的大作基本上不是从来没有在任天堂硬件上开发过独占作品，或者就是发行一个内容阉割过的版本”）。《福布斯》调查称2011年中最成功的前几款游戏（《[[上古卷轴V：天际|上古卷轴V：天际]]》，《[[质量效应3|质量效应3]]》，《[[傳送門2|傳送門2]]》，《[[黑色洛城|黑色洛城]]》，《[[戰地風雲3|戰地風雲3]]》，《[[決勝時刻：現代戰爭3|決勝時刻：現代戰爭3]]》）尽管都发布了个人电脑、Xbox 360和PlayStation 3版本，但其中只有《[[決勝時刻：現代戰爭3|決勝時刻：現代戰爭3]]》发布了Wii的版本，而其还是整个游戏系列中评价最低的一个版本。任天堂主机上的第三方游戏的缺乏的现象可能会在未来加剧，任天堂面临着“与游戏机周期内的竞争对手脱节的困境”；微软和索尼肯定会把他们的游戏机设计得比[[Wii_U|Wii U]]更强大。强大和丰富的第三方游戏被视为游戏机健康的重要标志。<ref name="theglobeandmail">{{cite news | url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/technology/video-games/controller-freak/whats-wrong-with-nintendo/article2219854/ | location=Toronto | work=The Globe and Mail | title=What's wrong with Nintendo? | date=2011-10-31 | access-date=2020-01-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302155609/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/technology/video-games/controller-freak/whats-wrong-with-nintendo/article2219854/ | archive-date=2012-03-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2012/04/26/nintendo-reports-461-2m-in-losses-is-selling-3ds-below-cost/ | title=Nintendo Reports $461.2M in Losses | work=Forbes | first=Paul | last=Tassi | date=2012-04-26 | access-date=2020-01-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729205949/https://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2012/04/26/nintendo-reports-461-2m-in-losses-is-selling-3ds-below-cost/ | archive-date=2017-07-29 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2012/05/10/sony-posts-record-losses-as-playstation-sales-drop/ | title=Cardiac Arrests At Sony, Nintendo As Consoles Show Their Age | work=Forbes | first=Paul | last=Tassi | date=2012-05-10 | access-date=2020-01-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729205903/https://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2012/05/10/sony-posts-record-losses-as-playstation-sales-drop/ | archive-date=2017-07-29 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

《[[环球邮报|环球邮报]]》，在解释任天堂为何在其2011-2012财年的前六个月创纪录地亏损了9.26亿美元的原因时，指责Wii的设计“目光短浅”。Wii在发布时获得了很大的成功，主要是因为它的售价并不昂贵（因为Wii的设计并不复杂），而且Wii的体感“游戏方式”较为新鲜。但是，随着在[[第七世代游戏机|第七世代游戏机]]中“用户的需求和周边硬件技术的不断发展”，这也意味着Wii的硬件将会很快过时，无法在长期的游戏机竞争中保持，如其更加先进竞争对手Xbox 360和PlayStation 3，它们被预计支持使用到2012–2013年。此外，Xbox 360和PlayStation 3后来的降价和体感控制外设的发布也逐渐抵消了Wii当年的优势。《环球邮报》认为，任天堂财务表现的不佳还有其他的原因，包括日元的走强、智能手机和平板电脑（如[[iPad|iPad]]）游戏的流行、以及人们对任天堂3DS掌机的反应的不温不火。<ref name="theglobeandmail" />

=={{anchor|系统销量}}销量==
[[File:Wii_sold_out.jpg|thumb]]上的[[HMV|HMV]]售罄]]
{{As of|2019|09|30}}，Wii在全球销售了1.0163亿台。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/en/sales/hard_soft/|title=IR Information : Sales Data - Hardware and Software Sales Units|work=Nintendo Co., Ltd.|access-date=2020-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024140433/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/en/sales/hard_soft/|archive-date=2016-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自推出以来，Wii的月销量就普遍高于其全球竞争对手。2006年11月28日，任天堂报告称，Wii在美国上市的头8天内售出了60多万台，使其成为任天堂在2017年发布任天堂Switch之前最大的主机上市。<ref name="wiisales">{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/747/747728p1.html|title=Wii Sells Through 600k|author=Hilary Goldstein|date=2006-11-27|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=2006-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061201234035/http://wii.ign.com/articles/747/747728p1.html|archive-date=2006-12-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/3/6/14836170/nintendo-switch-broke-sales-records-americas-zelda-two-day|title=The Switch broke Nintendo’s sales records (in the Americas, at least)|work=The Verge|date=2017-03-06|access-date=2018-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170307023109/http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/6/14836170/nintendo-switch-broke-sales-records-americas-zelda-two-day|archive-date=2017-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>日本最初共收到40万台Wii游戏机，<ref name="japanlaunch1">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/6200120.stm|title=Japanese Wii Sales Figures|date=2006-12-02|accessdate=2007-06-25|publisher=Kotaku|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070118053833/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/6200120.stm|archive-date=2007-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>并在发布两天内售出约37.2万台，其中Wii Sports和Wii Play是最畅销的游戏。<ref name="japanlaunch2">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=70728|title=Early Wii figures from Japan|website=Eurogamer|date=2006-12-06|accessdate=2006-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070211055742/http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=70728|archive-date=2007-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>任天堂2006年12月13日宣布，Wii在欧洲开售的两天内预计共售出32万5千台，在澳大利亚开售的前六天内已经售出了3万3千台，使其称为整个欧洲销售最快的游戏机和澳大利亚发售时销售速度最快游戏机。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/content_page.php?aid=21691|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061214203240/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/content_page.php?aid=21691|archive-date=2006-12-14|title=European consumers snap up 325,000 Wii consoles in two days // GamesIndustry.biz|date=2006-12-14|access-date=2018-09-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/12/13/nintendo-australia-breaks-30k-sales-record|title=Nintendo Australia Breaks 30k Sales Record|last=Kolan|first=Patrick|date=2006-12-13|website=IGN|language=en-US|access-date=2018-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904011414/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/12/13/nintendo-australia-breaks-30k-sales-record|archive-date=2018-09-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>到2006年底，Wii已经在全球售出了319万台。<ref name="earnings release Q4 2006">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2007/070125e.pdf#page=6|title=Consolidated Financial Highlights|date=2007-01-25|publisher=Nintendo|page=8|format=PDF|accessdate=2009-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070616233817/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2007/070125e.pdf#page=6|archive-date=2007-06-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根据[[NPD集团|NPD集团]]的数据，2007年上半年，Wii在美国的销量超过了Xbox 360和PlayStation 3销量的总和。<ref name="wiisalesUSA">{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2007/07/first-half-of-console-sales-for-2007-nintendo-the-big-winner-ps3-dead-last.ars|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070915005040/http://arstechnica.com/news.ars/post/20070724-first-half-of-console-sales-for-2007-nintendo-the-big-winner-ps3-dead-last.html|archivedate=2007-09-15|date=2007-07-24|first=Ben|last=Kuchera|title=Nintendo the big winner, PS3 dead last for the first half of 2007|website=Ars Technica|accessdate=2007-07-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>在日本市场，这一优势甚至更大，Wii在总销量上遥遥领先（从2007年11月发售到现在，Wii的每周的销量几乎都是两款主机的2:1<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.next-gen.biz/news/xbox-360-trumps-ps3-japan|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110815200311/http://www.next-gen.biz/news/xbox-360-trumps-ps3-japan|archivedate=2011-08-15|title=Xbox 360 Trumps PS3 in Japan|work=Edge|date=2007-11-09|accessdate=2007-11-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>到6:1<ref name="wiisalesJapan">{{cite web|url=http://wii.qj.net/Media-Create-sales-stats-July-9-15-Nintendo-continues-domination/pg/49/aid/98118|date=2007-07-21|author=Nicolo S.|title=Media Create sales stats (July 9–15): Nintendo continues domination|publisher=qj.net|accessdate=2007-08-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211065100/http://wii.qj.net/Media-Create-sales-stats-July-9-15-Nintendo-continues-domination/pg/49/aid/98118|archivedate=2009-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref> ）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=176131|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080609023356/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=176131|archivedate=2008-06-09|title=PS3 tops Wii in Japan... AGAIN|publisher=[[电脑与电子游戏|电脑与电子游戏]]|first=Mike|last=Jackson|date=2007-11-22|accessdate=2008-09-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>在澳大利亚，Wii打破了Xbox 360创下的纪录，成为澳大利亚历史上销售最快的游戏机，在游戏机发布的头四天里就卖出了32,901台。<ref name="wiibreaksxbox360record">{{cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/games/wii-breaks-xbox-sales-record/2006/12/14/1165685799546.html|date=2006-12-14|first=Asher|last=Moses|newspaper=[[雪梨晨鋒報|雪梨晨鋒報]]|title=Wii breaks Xbox 360 sales record|accessdate=2007-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071015015837/http://www.smh.com.au/news/games/wii-breaks-xbox-sales-record/2006/12/14/1165685799546.html|archive-date=2007-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>它还打破了Xbox 360在澳大利亚创下的最快销售10万台的纪录，Wii在6个月零2周内达到了这一里程碑。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/100000-wiis-sold-in-australia/1100-6172865/ |first=Randolph |last=Ramsay |title=100,000 Wiis sold in Australia |website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2007-06-21 |accessdate=2017-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107030048/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/100000-wiis-sold-in-australia/1100-6172865/ |archive-date=2017-11-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>Wii成为当时英国销售最快的游戏机，在发售后仅38周内就售出了100万台。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://nintendoplayers.com:80/article.php?articleID=1006|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071016161021/http://nintendoplayers.com/article.php?articleID=1006|archive-date=2007-10-16|title=Nintendo Players - Wii Sets UK Sales Record|date=2007-10-16|access-date=2018-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2007年9月12日，英国《[[金融时报_(英国)|金融时报]]》报道称，根据[[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]]、NPD集团和[[捷孚凯|捷孚凯]]的销售数据，Wii已经超过了一年前发布的Xbox 360，成为第七代家用游戏机的市场领导者。这是自[[超级任天堂|超级任天堂]]娱乐系统以来，任天堂游戏机首次引领其一代的销售。<ref name="wiileads">{{cite web|title=Nintendo Wii Outsells All Other Game Consoles|publisher=Ziff Davis|work=PC World|date=2007-09-12|url=https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2182666,00.asp|accessdate=2012-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902210705/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2182666,00.asp|archive-date=2012-09-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2007年7月11日，任天堂通告说，Wii在那一年中仍然会保持供不应求。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://money.cnn.com/2007/07/11/news/companies/wii/index.htm|publisher=CNN|date=2007-07-11|title=Christmas morn without a Wii?|accessdate=2008-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081015203916/http://money.cnn.com/2007/07/11/news/companies/wii/index.htm|archive-date=2008-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>在去年的12月，[[雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米|雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米]]透露，任天堂每月生产约180万台Wii游戏机。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abcnews.go.com/Technology/GadgetGuide/story?id=4001054&page=1|date=2007-12-18|title=Can't Find a Wii? Take a Rain Check|first=Ashley|last=Phililps|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=2008-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029030219/http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/GadgetGuide/story?id=4001054&page=1|archive-date=2008-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>2007年3月，英国的一些商店仍然缺少Wii库存，<ref name="UKWii Shortage March">{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/770/770565p1.html|title=UK Wiis "Like Gold Dust"|date=2007-03-06|accessdate=2007-04-18|website=IGN|first=Rob|last=Burman|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070316140618/http://wii.ign.com/articles/770/770565p1.html|archive-date=2007-03-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2007年6月，美国的需求数量仍然超过了Wii的供应数量，<ref name="USWii Shortage June">{{cite web |url=http://www.komonews.com/news/tech/8252247.html |title=Demand for Wii still outpaces supply |date=2007-06-29 |accessdate=2007-07-01 |publisher=komo-tv |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120507114232/http://www.komonews.com/news/tech/8252247.html |archivedate=2012-05-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2008年4月，加拿大的Wii游戏机“几乎在它碰到货架的那一瞬间就卖光了”。<ref name="CanadaNPD"/><ref name="CanadaNPD2"/>2008年10月，任天堂宣布，从10月到12月，Wii在北美的供应量将较2007年的水平大幅增加，<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.nintendo.ca/cgi-bin/usersite/display_info.cgi?lang=en&pageNum=9&id=1955846 |title=Nintendo's holiday 2008: Wii Speak Channel, Club Nintendo, more surprises |publisher=Nintendo |date=2008-10-02 |accessdate=2008-10-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081112130457/http://www.nintendo.ca/cgi-bin/usersite/display_info.cgi?lang=en |archivedate=2008-11-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>全球每月将生产240万台Wii（2007年为每月160万台）。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/oct/27/business/fi-nintendo27|title=Nintendo moves right along|first=Alex|last=Pham|newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|date=2008-10-27|accessdate=2008-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108043631/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/oct/27/business/fi-nintendo27|archive-date=2009-01-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

到2008年7月1日，Wii已经在美国卖出了1090万台，根据NPD集团的数据，它已经成为第七代家用游戏机的销售冠军（并且超过了Xbox 360）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/6194691.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013021113/http://www.gamespot.com/news/6194691.html|archivedate=2008-10-13|title=NPD: PS3 sales spike on MGS4|first=Tom|last=Magrino|date=2008-07-17|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2008-11-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.next-gen.biz/news/npd-wii-overtakes-360-us|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110815200337/http://www.next-gen.biz/news/npd-wii-overtakes-360-us|archivedate=2011-08-15|title=NPD: Wii Overtakes 360 in US|first=Joe|last=Keiser|magazine=[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]|date=2008-07-17|accessdate=2008-11-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/blogs/techchron/detail?blogid=19&entry_id=28286|title=E3: Nintendo Wii pulls ahead of Xbox 360 in console sales|first=Ryan|last=Kim|newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle|date=2008-07-17|accessdate=2008-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090918070154/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/blogs/techchron/detail?blogid=19&entry_id=28286|archive-date=2009-09-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在日本，Wii的销量在2008年1月就超过了[[GameCube|GameCube]]；<ref name=Japan2007>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=16914|title=Wii Sports Named Best Selling Game Of 2007 In Japan|last=Jenkins|first=David|date=2008-01-11|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|accessdate=2008-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080218025727/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=16914|archive-date=2008-02-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>据Enterbrain的数据，截至2008年12月，它已售出752万6821台。<ref name=Japan2008>{{cite web|url=http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1221045_1124.html|script-title=ja:2008年国内ゲーム市場規模は約5826億1000万円（エンターブレイン調べ）|work=[[Fami通|Fami通]]|publisher=[[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]]|language=ja|date=2009-01-05|accessdate=2009-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130085409/http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1221045_1124.html|archive-date=2009-01-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5123288/last-year-japanese-game-market-experienced-shrinkage|title=Last Year, Japanese Game Market Experienced Shrinkage|first=Brian|last=Ashcraft|publisher=Kotaku|date=2009-01-05|accessdate=2009-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122045647/http://kotaku.com/5123288/last-year-japanese-game-market-experienced-shrinkage|archive-date=2009-01-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>根据NPD集团的数据，Wii超越了Xbox 360成为加拿大最畅销的“下一代”家庭游戏机（截至2008年4月1日已售出81.3万台），并在此前17个月中13个月是最畅销的家庭游戏机。<ref name="CanadaNPD">{{cite press release|url=http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/April2008/17/c6749.html|title=Wii surpasses all other next generation consoles in lifetime sales|accessdate=2008-04-24|date=2008-04-17|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080420172921/http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/April2008/17/c6749.html|archive-date=2008-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CanadaNPD2">{{cite news|url= http://evergeek.thestar.com/news/2996.aspx|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080522144621/http://evergeek.thestar.com/news/2996.aspx|archivedate= 2008-05-22|title= NPD reports Nintendo Wii tops Canadian sales charts|date= 2008-04-22|work= Evergeek Media|publisher= [[多倫多星報|多倫多星報]]|accessdate= 2008-08-02|dead-url= yes}}</ref>根据NPD集团的数据，到2008年8月，Wii在加拿大共售出106万台，成为该国第7代家用游戏机销量突破百万大关的产品。根据GfK{{tsl|en|Chart-Track||Chart-Track}}，{{as of|2009|01|03|lc=y}}，Wii在英国的第七代游戏机销售中售出了490万台。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/console-installed-base-reaches-22m-in-uk|title=Console installed base reaches 22m in UK|first=Matt|last=Martin|work=[[Eurogamer|GamesIndustry.biz]]|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2009-01-13|accessdate=2009-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090118101038/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/console-installed-base-reaches-22m-in-uk|archive-date=2009-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/31902/Nintendo-rules-official-UK-hardware-figures|title=Nintendo rules official UK hardware figures|first=Tim|last=Ingham|date=2008-09-30|magazine={{tsl|en|MCV (magazine)||MCV}}|accessdate=2008-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081001202032/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/31902/Nintendo-rules-official-UK-hardware-figures|archive-date=2008-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2009年3月25日的[[游戏开发者大会|游戏开发者大会]]上，[[岩田聪|岩田聪]]称Wii的全球出货量已经达到了5000万台。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/6206693.html?tag=recent_news;title;1 |title=Nintendo's GDC conference |date=2009-03-25 |accessdate=2009-03-25 |first=Tor |last=Thorsen |website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090326162924/http://www.gamespot.com/news/6206693.html?tag=recent_news%3Btitle%3B1 |archivedate=2009-03-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>据澳大利亚捷孚凯的数据，Wii在澳大利亚发布84周内就在卖出了50多万台，超过了[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]和[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]，成为最快在澳大利亚累积50万台销量的游戏机。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/500000-wiis-sold-in-australia/1100-6194895/ |title=500,000 Wiis sold in Australia |first=James |last=Kozanecki |website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2008-07-23 |accessdate=2008-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107004036/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/500000-wiis-sold-in-australia/1100-6194895/ |archive-date=2017-11-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

当微软和索尼在低价亏损销售游戏机并希望能从软件销售中获得利润时，据报道任天堂已经优化了Wii的生产成本以在销售硬件中获得可观的利润率。<ref name="wiisalesprofit">{{cite web|url=http://seekingalpha.com/article/34357-game-console-wars-ii-nintendo-shaves-off-profits-leaving-competition-scruffy|date=2007-05-03|author=Roger Ehrenberg|title=Game Console Wars II: Nintendo Shaves Off Profits, Leaving Competition Scruffy|publisher=seekingalpha.com|accessdate=2007-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011070627/http://seekingalpha.com/article/34357-game-console-wars-ii-nintendo-shaves-off-profits-leaving-competition-scruffy|archive-date=2007-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>2007年9月17日，英国《金融时报》报道，Wii的每台直接利润可能有所不同，从日本的13美元到美国的49美元，再到欧洲的79美元。<ref name="wiiunitsprofit">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/features/report-nintendo-makes-about-49-per-wii-sold-in-us/70921/?biz=1|date=2007-09-17|first=James|last=Brightman|title=Report: Nintendo Makes About $49 Per Wii Sold in U.S|publisher=gamingdaily.BIZ|accessdate=2007-09-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100815075610/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/features/report-nintendo-makes-about-49-per-wii-sold-in-us/70921/?biz=1|archivedate=2010-08-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>2008年12月2日，《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》报道称，任天堂每卖出一台Wii游戏机就能获得6美元的营业利润。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/6201833.html|title=Report: Nintendo banks $6 on each Wii sold|first=Tom|last=Magrino|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2008-12-02|accessdate=2008-12-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100815075610/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/features/report-nintendo-makes-about-49-per-wii-sold-in-us/70921/?biz=1|archivedate=2010-08-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年9月23日，任天堂首次宣布Wii降价。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/corporate/release/2009/090924.html |title=ニュースリリース：2009年9月24日 |publisher=Nintendo.co.jp |date=2009-09-24 |accessdate=2010-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629122916/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/corporate/release/2009/090924.html |archive-date=2011-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年12月，任天堂在美国卖出了300多万台Wii游戏机，创下了当月的地区纪录，结束了连续9个月销售下滑的局面，原因是Wii的降价和《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》等游戏软件的发布。<ref>{{cite magazine| author= Pavel Alpeyev| date= 2010-01-05| title= Nintendo Shares Rise After Record Wii Sales in U.S| magazine= [[彭博商业周刊|彭博商业周刊]]| url= http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-01-05/nintendo-shares-rise-after-record-wii-sales-in-u-s-update2-.html| accessdate= 2010-01-05| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100110004944/http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-01-05/nintendo-shares-rise-after-record-wii-sales-in-u-s-update2-.html| archivedate= 2010-01-10| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| author= Kiyoshi Takenaka| date= 2010-01-05| title= Nintendo Wii posts record U.S. sales in Dec| work= Reuters| url= https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTOE6040A420100105| accessdate= 2010-02-27| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100526192555/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTOE6040A420100105| archive-date= 2010-05-26| dead-url= no}}</ref>2010年1月31日，Wii成为任天堂最畅销的家用游戏机，销量超过6700万台，超过了原来的[[红白机|红白机]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/01/28/ds-sells-125-million-worldwide-wii-up-to-67-million/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100130202125/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/01/28/ds-sells-125-million-worldwide-wii-up-to-67-million/|archive-date=2010-01-30|title=DS sells 125 million worldwide, Wii up to 67 million|date=2010-01-30|access-date=2018-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年，Wii的销量开始下滑，比前一年下降了21%。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://kotaku.com/5532274/wii-sales-down-21-in-a-single-year?comment=22699923|title=Wii Sales Down 21% In A Single Year|last=Plunkett|first=Luke|work=Kotaku|date=2010-05-06|access-date=2018-09-01|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901215845/https://kotaku.com/5532274/wii-sales-down-21-in-a-single-year?comment=22699923|archive-date=2018-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii在2011年继续下滑，任天堂的季度收入下降了41%。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tomsguide.com/us/quarterly-earnings-q3-2011-wii-ds-3ds,news-13020.html|title=Nintendo Hit With Dramatic Decline in Sales|date=2011-10-27|work=Tom's Guide|access-date=2018-09-01|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902011901/https://www.tomsguide.com/us/quarterly-earnings-q3-2011-wii-ds-3ds,news-13020.html|archive-date=2018-09-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管销售放缓，但任天堂报告称，2011年的“黑色星期五”售出了50多万台Wii游戏机，成为Wii历史上最成功的“黑色星期五”。<ref name="post">{{cite news |title=Nintendo Wii has biggest-ever Black Friday, new Zelda game sets sales record |work=Boy Genius Report |date=2011-12-01 |url=http://www.bgr.com/2011/12/01/nintendo-wii-has-biggest-ever-black-friday-new-zelda-game-sets-sales-record/ |access-date=2020-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404212537/https://bgr.com/2011/12/01/nintendo-wii-has-biggest-ever-black-friday-new-zelda-game-sets-sales-record/ |archive-date=2019-04-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>Wii的销量在2012年进一步下滑，比2011年下降了一半。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.engadget.com/2012/07/25/nintendo-q1-results-wii-sales-cut-in-half-since-2011-but-3ds-s/|title=Nintendo Q1 results: Wii sales cut in half since 2011, but 3DS sales more than double|work=Engadget|access-date=2018-09-01|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901215810/https://www.engadget.com/2012/07/25/nintendo-q1-results-wii-sales-cut-in-half-since-2011-but-3ds-s/|archive-date=2018-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年12月7日，Wii Mini在加拿大上市的头两个月售出了3万5700台。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/03/01/wii-mini-sells-35-700-units-in-canada-across-first-two-months/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130304072748/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/03/01/wii-mini-sells-35-700-units-in-canada-across-first-two-months/|archive-date=2013-03-04|title=Wii Mini sells 35,700 units in Canada across first two months|work=Joystiq|date=2013-03-04|access-date=2018-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/ONIEEqvK1pbPyTbW2lWO6QnPUiqqvuuI|title=NINTENDO INTRODUCES NEW Wii MINI THAT'S ALL ABOUT THE GAMES - Nintendo Official Site|work=Nintendo.com|access-date=2018-08-10|language=en-us|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180810074012/https://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/ONIEEqvK1pbPyTbW2lWO6QnPUiqqvuuI|archive-date=2018-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年6月30日，Wii的销量超过了1亿台，在2013年3月至6月间的销量达到了21万台。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.gamezone.com/news/wii-lifetime-sales-surpass-100-million-units/|title=Wii lifetime sales surpass 100 million units - GameZone|date=2013-07-31|work=GameZone|access-date=2018-08-07|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807033441/https://www.gamezone.com/news/wii-lifetime-sales-surpass-100-million-units/|archive-date=2018-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==法律问题==
<!--{{See also|Wii Remote#Legal issues|l1=Legal issues of the Wii Remote}}-->

Wii游戏机、Wii遥控器和其他配件曾被提起过诉讼。

2006年6月，[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]的公司Lonestar Inventions，L.P.起诉任天堂，称该公司抄袭了Lonestar的一款[[电容器|电容器]]专利设计，并将其用于Wii游戏机。<ref name="RECAP2">{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2007/06/18/lonestar-sues-nintendo-over-wii-capacitor-design/|title=Lonestar sues Nintendo over Wii capacitor design|last=Quilty-Harper|first=Conrad|date=2006-06-18|publisher=Engadget/Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2007-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070620161126/http://www.engadget.com/2007/06/18/lonestar-sues-nintendo-over-wii-capacitor-design/|archive-date=2007-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/gov.uscourts.txed.103593|title=gov.uscourts.txed.103593|others=RECAP Project|accessdate=2018-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404221750/https://archive.org/details/gov.uscourts.txed.103593|archive-date=2019-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>后来Lonestar同意在2009年7月20日前驳回所有指控，并与提供任天堂微处理器技术的AMD达成和解；任天堂和Lonestar是否有庭外和解条款尚不清楚。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.law360.com/articles/111968/lonestar-amd-settle-ip-suit-over-nintendo-wii-chip|title=Lonestar, AMD Settle IP Suit Over Nintendo Wii Chip|last=Davis|first=Ryan|date=2009-07-17|work={{tsl|en|Law360||Law360}}|accessdate=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228232545/https://www.law360.com/articles/111968/lonestar-amd-settle-ip-suit-over-nintendo-wii-chip|archive-date=2017-12-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="RECAP2"/>

德克萨斯州的Anascape有限公司在2006年夏天就任天堂控制器使用的振动反馈提起了专利侵权诉讼。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/933/1027933/microsoft-nintendo-sued-over-games-controller|title=Microsoft, Nintendo sued over games controller|date=2006-08-03|publisher=The Inquirer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071226182628/http://www.theinquirer.net/en/inquirer/news/2006/08/03/microsoft-nintendo-sued-over-games-controller|archivedate=2007-12-26|accessdate=2006-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>2008年7月的一项裁决禁止任天堂在美国销售经典控制器，此外还有GameCube和Wavebird控制器。2010年4月22日，在向[[美国联邦巡回区上诉法院|美国联邦巡回区上诉法院]]提出上诉后，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.gamespot.com/forums/system-wars-314159282/nintendo-faces-ban-on-some-wii-controllers-26503822/|title=Nintendo Faces Ban on Some Wii, GameCube Controllers (Update2)|last=Decker|first=Susan|date=2008-07-22|accessdate=2008-09-25|publisher=Bloomberg.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160209032858/http://www.gamespot.com/forums/system-wars-314159282/nintendo-faces-ban-on-some-wii-controllers-26503822/|archive-date=2016-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>联邦巡回法院做出了对任天堂有利的裁决。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.courthousenews.com/2010/04/22/26649.htm|title=Nintendo Wins Patent Dispute Over Controllers|website=www.courthousenews.com|date=2010-04-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100823191844/http://www.courthousenews.com/2010/04/22/26649.htm|archivedate=2010-08-23|accessdate=2020-01-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2006年12月，{{tsl|en|Interlink Electronics||Interlink Electronics}}有限公司就Wii遥控器的指向功能对任天堂提起了专利侵权诉讼，称任天堂的“侵权行为导致合理的版税损失、销售额减少和/或利润损失”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/750/750001p1.html|title=Nintendo Sued for Patent Infringement|last=Seff|first=Micah|date=2006-12-08|website=IGN|accessdate=2006-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061213042423/http://wii.ign.com/articles/750/750001p1.html|archive-date=2006-12-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="RECAP">{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/gov.uscourts.ded.37438|title=gov.uscourts.ded.37438|others=RECAP Project|accessdate=2018-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404221749/https://archive.org/details/gov.uscourts.ded.37438|archive-date=2019-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该诉讼于2007年3月被Interlink驳回。<ref name="RECAP"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://archive.org/details/gov.uscourts.ded.37438|title=Case docket: Interlink Electronics Inc. v. Nintendo of America|website=ia800200.us.archive.org|accessdate=2018-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404221749/https://archive.org/details/gov.uscourts.ded.37438|archive-date=2019-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2008年8月，Hillcrest Laboratories公司和[[美国国际贸易委员会|美国国际贸易委员会]]向美国司法部起诉了任天堂。称Wii遥控器侵犯了它的三项专利。据称，还有第四个Hillcrest专利（用于电视屏幕上显示的图形界面）也遭到了侵犯。Hillcrest寻求禁止Wii游戏机进口美国，<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB121925111060757011|title=Start-Up Says Nintendo Violated Patents|last=Wingfield|first=Nick|date=2008-08-21|accessdate=2008-09-25|publisher=online.wsj.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217082827/http://www.wsj.com/articles/SB121925111060757011|archive-date=2014-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年8月24日，任天堂和Hillcrest达成协议，但协议条款没有公开披露。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theage.com.au/world/nintendo-settles-us-trade-fight-over-wii-20090825-ewno.html|title=Nintendo settles US trade fight over Wii|date=2009-08-24|work=www.theage.com.au|accessdate=2009-08-24|publisher=[[世纪报|世纪报]]|location=Melbourne}}</ref>

2008年11月，<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dockets.justia.com/docket/texas/txedce/6:2008cv00429/112889|title=Motiva LLC v. Nintendo Co Ltd et al|website=Justia Dockets & Filings|language=en|access-date=2018-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829212031/https://dockets.justia.com/docket/texas/txedce/6:2008cv00429/112889|archive-date=2018-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>Motiva LLC向美国国际贸易委员会对任天堂提起诉讼，称Wii侵犯了该公司的跟踪人体运动和姿势的两项专利。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.kotaku.co.uk/2017/09/07/nintendos-long-history-of-beating-patent-lawsuits|title=Nintendo's Long History of Beating Patent Lawsuits|website=Kotaku UK|language=en|date=2017-09-07|access-date=2018-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630083151/http://www.kotaku.co.uk/2017/09/07/nintendos-long-history-of-beating-patent-lawsuits|archive-date=2018-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年1月，美国国际贸易委员会裁定支持任天堂，声称“Motiva的诉讼是针对它自己的财务收益，而不是鼓励采用Motiva的专利技术，”,“在成功起诉任天堂之后，Motiva的专利技术根本不可能得到合作伙伴的许可。”。委员会还裁定，任天堂没有侵犯Motiva的任何专利。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-nintendo-motiva-decision-idUSBRE94C0WJ20130513|title=Nintendo wins appeals court decision over Wii|last=Stempel|first=Jonathan|work=Reuters|date=2013-05-14|access-date=2018-07-01|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702044011/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-nintendo-motiva-decision-idUSBRE94C0WJ20130513|archive-date=2018-07-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年9月，ThinkOptics公司就任天堂的遥控器向[[美国德克萨斯东区联邦地区法院|美国德克萨斯东区联邦地区法院]]提起诉讼，称Wii侵犯了其专利的Wavit Remote，这些专利分别是“基于手持视觉的绝对指向系统”、“基于手持视觉的绝对指向系统的手持设备”和“基于手持视觉的绝对指向系统”，这些专利构成了Wavit Remote的基础。他们还表示，Wii U也侵犯了他们的专利，并声称任天堂已经意识到Wii侵犯了ThinkOptics的专利。该诉讼要求法院颁布[[禁制令|禁制令]]，禁止侵犯产品、[[权利金|权利金]]、 {{tsl|en|attorney's fee||律师费}}和利润损失。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://techcrunch.com/2011/09/07/nintendo-gets-sued-over-the-wii/|title=Nintendo Gets Sued Over The Wii|work=TechCrunch|date=2011-09-08|access-date=2018-09-05|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905065311/https://techcrunch.com/2011/09/07/nintendo-gets-sued-over-the-wii/|archive-date=2018-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.law360.com/texas/articles/269491/thinkoptics-sues-nintendo-over-remote-control-patents|title=ThinkOptics Sues Nintendo Over Remote Control Patents - Law360|website=www.law360.com|language=en|date=2011-09-06|access-date=2018-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905102104/https://www.law360.com/texas/articles/269491/thinkoptics-sues-nintendo-over-remote-control-patents|archive-date=2018-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年8月，该诉讼被ThinkOptics驳回。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://insight.rpxcorp.com/lit/txedce-132096-thinkoptics-v-nintendo-of-america|title=ThinkOptics, Inc v. Nintendo of America, Inc. et al|website=insight.rpxcorp.com|access-date=2018-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905065249/https://insight.rpxcorp.com/lit/txedce-132096-thinkoptics-v-nintendo-of-america|archive-date=2018-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>

从2012年12月开始，iLife Technologies公司对几家大公司提起了专利侵权诉讼，指控它们侵犯了一组专利，这些专利涉及“评估机构相对于环境的移动的系统和方法”，其主要针对的是医疗领域；2013年12月，任天堂被iLife起诉，称Wii遥控器侵犯了他们的专利。该诉讼要求1.44亿美元的损害赔偿，依据是该公司迄今为止售出的3600万台Wii和Wii U游戏机每台罚款4美元。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasobserver.com/news/a-dallas-inventor-is-suing-nintendo-for-stealing-his-idea-for-wii-us-motion-sensors-7124540|title=A Dallas Inventor Is Suing Nintendo for Stealing His Idea for Wii U's Motion Sensors|last=Nicholson|first=Eric|date=2013-12-16|work={{tsl|en|Dallas Observer||Dallas Observer}}|accessdate=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171229052238/http://www.dallasobserver.com/news/a-dallas-inventor-is-suing-nintendo-for-stealing-his-idea-for-wii-us-motion-sensors-7124540|archive-date=2017-12-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年8月进行了陪审团庭审，陪审团做出了有利于iLife Technologies的裁决，任天堂被迫支付了1010万美元的赔偿金。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2017/09/jury-finds-nintendo-wii-infringes-dallas-inventors-patent-awards-10m/|title=Jury finds Nintendo Wii infringes Dallas inventor’s patent, awards $10M|last=Mullin|first=Joe|date=2017-09-01|work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|accessdate=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171229052307/https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2017/09/jury-finds-nintendo-wii-infringes-dallas-inventors-patent-awards-10m/|archive-date=2017-12-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>虽然任天堂对这一决定提出了上诉，但[[美国联邦上诉法院|美国联邦上诉法院]]在2017年12月维持了陪审团的决定。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/glixel/news/appeals-court-upholds-ilife-patent-in-10m-wii-gaming-judgment-w514792|title=Appeals Court Upholds iLife Patent in $10M Wii Gaming Judgment|date=2017-12-28|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]|accessdate=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228155104/https://www.rollingstone.com/glixel/news/appeals-court-upholds-ilife-patent-in-10m-wii-gaming-judgment-w514792|archive-date=2017-12-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===腕带===
Wii遥控器的腕带也是个问题。

2006年12月中旬，Green Welling LLP律师事务所对任天堂“有缺陷的腕带”提起了[[集体诉讼|集体诉讼]]。几天后，任天堂宣布[[產品召回|召回]]这款腕带的产品，并发布了一款新版本的腕带，改进了腕带的安全保护机制，导致后来的诉讼被撤销。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chron.com/news/article/BW-Nintendo-Recalls-Defective-Wii-Wrist-Straps-1850489.php|title=Nintendo Recalls Defective Wii Wrist Straps After Class Action Filed by Green Welling LLP|date=2006-12-16|accessdate=2007-03-23|publisher=Business Wire|via=[[休斯敦纪事报|Houston Chronicle]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703150147/http://www.chron.com/news/article/BW-Nintendo-Recalls-Defective-Wii-Wrist-Straps-1850489.php|archive-date=2015-07-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://kotaku.com/5108362/nintendo-faces-new-remote-strap-lawsuit|title=Nintendo Faces New Remote Strap Lawsuit|last=Fahey|first=Mike|date=2008-12-12|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|accessdate=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171229052300/https://kotaku.com/5108362/nintendo-faces-new-remote-strap-lawsuit|archive-date=2017-12-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2008年12月，一位母亲在科罗拉多州提起了第二起集体诉讼，称升级后的腕带仍然存在问题。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/3725869/Nintendo-sued-over-dangerous-Wii-controllers.html|title=Nintendo sued over 'dangerous' Wii controllers|last=Beaumont|first=Claudine|date=2008-12-12|work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]|accessdate=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171229000800/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/3725869/Nintendo-sued-over-dangerous-Wii-controllers.html|archive-date=2017-12-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>这起诉讼在2010年9月被驳回，因为任天堂发现，根据科罗拉多州消费者保护法，腕带并非故意有缺陷。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.law360.com/articles/196315/nintendo-sends-wii-safety-strap-case-packing|title=Nintendo Sends Wii Safety Strap Case Packing|last=Howard|first=Samual|date=2010-09-24|work={{tsl|en|Law360||Law360}}|accessdate=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228232710/https://www.law360.com/articles/196315/nintendo-sends-wii-safety-strap-case-packing|archive-date=2017-12-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===商标===
2000年，“{{tsl|en|Weemote||Weemote}}”一词被总部位于[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]的电视遥控器制造商Fobis Technologies注册为商标，后来被用作他们为儿童设计的遥控器的名字。<ref name="time">{{cite web|url=http://www.time.com/time/business/article/0,8599,1824499,00.html|title=The Weemote vs. Wiimote Tiff|author=Padgett, Tim|date=2008-07-18|work=TIME.com|accessdate=2008-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080808075839/http://www.time.com/time/business/article/0,8599,1824499,00.html|archive-date=2008-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.remotecentral.com/weemote/index.html|title=RC: Fobis Technologies Weemote Kids' Remote Control Review (1)|website=www.remotecentral.com|access-date=2018-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803112619/http://www.remotecentral.com/weemote/index.html|archive-date=2018-08-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>虽然拼写不同，但“Weemote”的发音与“Wiimote”完全相同，Wiimote是Wii遥控器的非官方名称。<ref name="time" /><ref name="gp1">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepolitics.com/2008/07/23/small-firm039s-weemote-came-first-steamrolled-nintendo039s-wiimote|title=Small Firm's Weemote Came First, But Steamrolled by Nintendo's Wiimote|date=2008-07-23|work=GamePolitics.com|accessdate=2008-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080730052700/http://www.gamepolitics.com/2008/07/23/small-firm039s-weemote-came-first-steamrolled-nintendo039s-wiimote|archive-date=2008-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于与Wiimote混淆，Weemote的销量出现了下滑。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.time.com:80/time/business/article/0,8599,1824499,00.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080808075839/http://www.time.com/time/business/article/0,8599,1824499,00.html|archive-date=2008-08-08|title=The Weemote vs. Wiimote Tiff - TIME|date=2008-08-08|access-date=2018-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2008年，Weemote的总销量不足100万。Fobis Technologies称“Wiimote”是{{tsl|en|trademark infringement||商标侵权}}，虽然许多零售商使用这一术语，但任天堂官方并未正式使用。<ref name="gp1" />Fobis向零售商发出了多达100封[[停止并终止|停止并终止]]函，并提出向任天堂出售这一商标；任天堂拒绝了这一请求，并回应称，该公司“没有使用Weemote商标，也不打算使用”。<ref name="gp2">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepolitics.com/2008/07/24/nintendo-comments-weemote-wiimote-flap-online-retailer-pressured|title=Nintendo Comments on Weemote-Wiimote Flap; Online Retailer Pressured|date=2008-07-24|work=GamePolitics.com|accessdate=2008-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080730052718/http://www.gamepolitics.com/2008/07/24/nintendo-comments-weemote-wiimote-flap-online-retailer-pressured|archive-date=2008-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Wii的商标申请是在2006年提出的，但直到2010年7月才被美国政府注册。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://kotaku.com/5599903/wii-is-now-a-registered-trademark|title=Wii Is Now a Registered Trademark|last=Totilo|first=Stephen|work=Kotaku|date=2010-07-29|access-date=2018-07-22|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723003643/https://kotaku.com/5599903/wii-is-now-a-registered-trademark|archive-date=2018-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Wii遥控器（Wii Remote）的商标申请在2008年3月被美国专利商标局驳回。[[美国专利及商标局|美国专利及商标局]]表示，“遥控器（remote）”这个词很常用，因此不应该注册为商标。美国专利商标局表示，如果任天堂放弃“遥控器（remote）”一词的专有权，即“遥控器（remote）”一词只会在营销和手册中出现在“Wii”单词之后，他们将接受任天堂的商标申请；“Wii遥控器（Wii Remote）”商标于2012年7月被接受。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.engadget.com/2008/12/02/wee-bit-of-trouble-nintendo-cant-trademark-wii-remote/|title=Wee bit of trouble: Nintendo can't trademark 'Wii Remote'|work=Engadget|date=2008-12-02|access-date=2018-08-29|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829175412/https://www.engadget.com/2008/12/02/wee-bit-of-trouble-nintendo-cant-trademark-wii-remote/|archive-date=2018-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://trademarks.justia.com/774/27/wii-77427250.html|title=WII REMOTE Trademark of Nintendo of America Inc. - Registration Number 4177430 - Serial Number 77427250|website=Justia Trademarks|language=en|access-date=2018-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829175411/https://trademarks.justia.com/774/27/wii-77427250.html|archive-date=2018-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==其他机型==

===RVL-101===
[[File:WiiFamilyEdition.svg|thumb]]

'''RVL-101'''机型是在Wii主机系列生命周期后期发布的一个降低成本的版本，其去掉了所有任天堂GameCube功能，并缺少了原来机型上的任天堂GameCube控制器控制器端口和记忆卡插槽。另外，它也没有附带支架，因为它被设计为只能水平放置。该游戏机于2011年8月17日公布，并于2011年10月23日在美国和2011年11月4日在欧洲发售。<ref name="Wii2.0" /><ref name="EUFamily"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/31328/newsnew-black-wii-bundle-includes-mario-cd/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111114130448/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/31328/newsnew-black-wii-bundle-includes-mario-cd/|archive-date=2011-11-14|title=Wii News: New black Wii bundle includes Mario CD - Official Nintendo Magazine|date=2011-11-14|access-date=2018-08-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在欧洲发售时，它附带一个[[Wii遙控器|Wii遥控器Plus]]、《[[Wii_Party|Wii Party]]》和《[[Wii_Sports|Wii Sports]]》。<ref name="Wii2.0">{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/new-slim-wii-announced-won-t-play-gamecube-games-209100.phtml|publisher=Destructoid|title=New slim Wii announced, won't play GameCube games|date=2011-08-17|accessdate=2011-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901210331/http://www.destructoid.com/new-slim-wii-announced-won-t-play-gamecube-games-209100.phtml|archive-date=2011-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/nintendo-no-plans-for-slim-wii-in-north-america-209130.phtml|publisher=Destructoid|title=Nintendo: No plans for slim Wii in North America|date=2011-08-17|accessdate=2011-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901211648/http://www.destructoid.com/nintendo-no-plans-for-slim-wii-in-north-america-209130.phtml|archive-date=2011-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/29791/new-wii-is-same-size-as-old-wii/ |title=New Wii is same size as old Wii |magazine=Official Nintendo Magazine |date=2011-08-23 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928121842/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/29791/new-wii-is-same-size-as-old-wii/ |archivedate=2011-09-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/2011/nintendo_announces_packed_2011_line-up_of_upcoming_games_44323.html|title=Nintendo announces packed 2011 line-up of upcoming games|date=2011-08-17|publisher=Nintendo|accessdate=2011-08-17}}</ref>主机以白色机型发售，后来于2011年10月23日又发售了一款黑色的机型，并与《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》和官方《[[超级马里奥银河|超级马里奥银河]]》音轨一同出售。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mynintendonews.com/2011/10/11/nintendo-wii-black-wii-holiday-bundle-with-new-super-mario-bros-wii-and-exclusive-mario-music-cd/ |title=Nintendo Wii: Black Wii Holiday Bundle With New Super Mario Bros Wii And Exclusive Mario Music CD |publisher=My Nintendo News |date=2011-10-11 |access-date=2020-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404212603/https://mynintendonews.com/2011/10/11/nintendo-wii-black-wii-holiday-bundle-with-new-super-mario-bros-wii-and-exclusive-mario-music-cd/ |archive-date=2019-04-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年11月18日，该机型还在2012年的“黑色星期五”和《[[马里奥和索尼克在伦敦2012奥运会|马里奥和索尼克在伦敦2012奥运会]]》游戏同时发布发布了一款蓝色机型，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mynintendonews.com/2011/10/10/nintendo-wii-nintendo-is-releasing-a-blue-wii-console-in-november/ |title=Nintendo Wii: Nintendo Is Releasing A Blue Wii Console In November |publisher=My Nintendo News |date=2011-10-10 |accessdate=2011-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111011175424/http://mynintendonews.com/2011/10/10/nintendo-wii-nintendo-is-releasing-a-blue-wii-console-in-november/ |archive-date=2011-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年底，任天堂在北美发布了另外一种黑色套装，内含一张同时包含《Wii Sports》和《[[Wii運動_度假勝地|Wii運動 度假勝地]]》游戏的光盘，而不是之前的《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》游戏和《超级马里奥银河》原声带。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://news.yahoo.com/nintendo-wii-now-bundled-wii-sports-price-slashed-015348111.html |title=Nintendo Wii now bundled with Wii Sports, price slashed to just $129 |website=Yahoo |date=2011-10-15 |access-date=2020-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404212533/https://news.yahoo.com/nintendo-wii-now-bundled-wii-sports-price-slashed-015348111.html |archive-date=2019-04-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

