===RVL-201（Wii Mini）{{anchor|Wii Mini}}===
{{Main|Wii Mini}}

[[File:Nintendo-Wii-Mini-Console-FL.jpg|thumb]]

'''Wii Mini'''（写为Wii mini）是一款体积更小、经过重新设计的Wii，配有一个上置开合式光盘驱动器。它于2012年11月27日发布，并于2012年12月7日在加拿大发布，建议零售价为99.99[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]。<ref name="NinWiiMini">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/ONIEEqvK1pbPyTbW2lWO6QnPUiqqvuuI|title=Nintendo introduces Wii Mini that's all about games|publisher=Nintendo of Canada|date=2012-11-22|accessdate=2012-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180810074012/https://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/ONIEEqvK1pbPyTbW2lWO6QnPUiqqvuuI|archive-date=2018-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>该机型随后于2013年3月22日在欧洲发布，<ref name="web.archive.org">{{Cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com.au/gaming/news/a461694/wii-mini-confirmed-for-europe-launching-next-month.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907235732/http://www.digitalspy.com.au/gaming/news/a461694/wii-mini-confirmed-for-europe-launching-next-month.html|archive-date=2015-09-07|title=Wii Mini confirmed for Europe, launching next month - Gaming News - Digital Spy|date=2015-09-07|access-date=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref> 并于2013年11月17日在美国发布。<ref name="Wii mini Official Site - Buy Now">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/wiimini/buynow/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107012351/https://www.nintendo.com/wiimini/buynow/|archive-date=2013-11-07|title=Wii mini Official Site - Buy Now|date=2013-11-07|access-date=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>该机型没有在日本、澳大利亚或新西兰上映。这款游戏机没有[[色差端子|色差端子]]（色差视频/[[D端子|D端子]]、[[S-端子|S-端子]]和RGB {{tsl|en|SCART||SCART}}）输出、不支持兼容GameCube、在线功能的连接、[[SD卡|SD卡]]的插槽和[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]的支持，而且相较于先前机型的两个，其只有一个[[USB|USB]]接口。<ref name=EurogamerReview>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/df-hardware-nintendo-wii-mini-review|title=Nintendo Wii Mini review|last=Leadbetter|first=Richard|date=2012-12-12|work=Eurogamer|accessdate=2012-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121215091852/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/df-hardware-nintendo-wii-mini-review|archive-date=2012-12-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=WiiMiniManual>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/downloads/WiiMiniOpMn_RVO_en.pdf|title=Nintendo Wii Mini Operations Manual|publisher=Nintendo of America|page=10|accessdate=2012-12-16|quote=The Wii Mini console will not work with any AV cable other than the model supplied.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130118214640/http://www.nintendo.com/consumer/downloads/WiiMiniOpMn_RVO_en.pdf|archive-date=2013-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>最初发售的机型没有附带任何游戏，但从2013年9月18日起，在加拿大出售的Wii Mini内附《[[瑪利歐賽車Wii|瑪利歐賽車Wii]]》，<ref>{{cite web |title=Mario Kart Wii picture |publisher=Future Shop |url=http://www.futureshop.ca/multimedia/Products/500x500/102/10270/10270488.jpg |date=2013-09-18 |accessdate=2013-09-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131003015233/http://www.futureshop.ca/multimedia/Products/500x500/102/10270/10270488.jpg |archivedate=2013-10-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>并在后来于美国也开始提供。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tomsguide.com/us/nintendo-wii-mini-pros-cons,news-17823.html|title=Should You Buy a Wii Mini? -- Tom's Guide|date=2013-11-05|work=Tom's Guide|access-date=2018-08-31|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831035527/https://www.tomsguide.com/us/nintendo-wii-mini-pros-cons,news-17823.html|archive-date=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>任天堂利用这款游戏机和{{tsl|en|Nintendo Selects||任天堂Selects}}系列游戏来推广低成本游戏。Wii Mini采用哑光黑色和红色边框设计，包装内含一个红色的Wii遥控器Plus和Nunchuk、[[AV端子|复合视频]]/音频电缆、传感条和电源适配器。<ref name=EngadgetMini>{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2012/12/06/nintendo-wii-mini-hands-on/|title=Nintendo Wii Mini hands-on|last=Fingas|first=Jon|date=2012-12-06|work=Engadget|publisher=AOL|accessdate=2012-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121209013632/http://www.engadget.com/2012/12/06/nintendo-wii-mini-hands-on/|archive-date=2012-12-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==继承者==
{{Main|Wii U}}

任天堂在{{tsl|en|E3 2011||2011年E3展}}上宣布了Wii的继任者[[Wii_U|Wii U]]。<ref name=Telegraph>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/nintendo/8563836/Nintendos-Wii-U-unveiled-at-E3-keeping-Nintendos-revolution-going.html|title=Nintendo's Wii U unveiled at E3: keeping Nintendo's revolution going|date=2012-06-08|accessdate=2012-09-13|newspaper=Telegraph|first=Tom|last=Hoggins|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120611023334/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/nintendo/8563836/Nintendos-Wii-U-unveiled-at-E3-keeping-Nintendos-revolution-going.html|archive-date=2012-06-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii U的[[Wii_U控制器|控制器]]拥有一块触摸屏，主机能够输出[[1080p|1080p]]高清图像；它完全向后兼容的Wii游戏和外设。Wii遥控器，双节棍控制器和平衡板等控制器也与Wii U游戏兼容并被支持。<ref name=ET>{{cite web|url=http://www.extremetech.com/gaming/136121-nintendo-confirms-wii-u-specs-and-release-date-prices-it-above-xbox-360-and-ps3|title=Nintendo confirms Wii U specs and release date, prices it above Xbox 360 and PS3|date=2012-09-13|accessdate=2012-09-13|publisher=Extreme Tech|first=Sebastian|last=Anthony|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120915231046/http://www.extremetech.com/gaming/136121-nintendo-confirms-wii-u-specs-and-release-date-prices-it-above-xbox-360-and-ps3|archive-date=2012-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii U于2012年11月18日在北美发售，11月30日在欧洲、澳大利亚和新西兰发售，12月8日在日本发售，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/13/wii-u-price-release-date-announced|title=Wii U Price, Release Date Announced|last=Goldfarb|first=Andrew|date=2012-09-13|website=IGN|language=en-US|access-date=2018-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723034736/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/13/wii-u-price-release-date-announced|archive-date=2018-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>11月26日在[[巴西|巴西]]发售。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://nintendotoday.com/brazil-finally-getting-wii-u/|title=Brazil finally gets the Wii U, will cost R$1899 - NintendoToday|date=2013-11-08|work=NintendoToday|access-date=2018-07-22|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723034426/http://nintendotoday.com/brazil-finally-getting-wii-u/|archive-date=2018-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>Wii U于2017年1月31日在全球停产。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://kotaku.com/wii-u-production-has-officially-ended-for-japan-1791813878|title=Wii U Production Has Officially Ended For Japan [Update]|last=Ashcraft|first=Brian|work=Kotaku|date=2017-01-31|access-date=2018-06-19|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619170148/https://kotaku.com/wii-u-production-has-officially-ended-for-japan-1791813878|archive-date=2018-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>

